# game/day 6.rpy:66
translate chinese_simplified day06_a06babf4:

    # fn "「Hmm, what to do today...」"
    fn "「今天做什么呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:70
translate chinese_simplified day06_5eb9ac70:

    # "I stretch out my back as I say that.{w} Even though thatlazy feeling is coming back, {w=.3}I want to make the most\nof my homecoming and go somewhere."
    "说着用力伸了伸懒腰。{w}从回来这里之后就几乎每天都在出门，{w=.3}不过难得回到故乡，当然就想每个地方都去看看嘛。"

# game/day 6.rpy:71
translate chinese_simplified day06_86d7d2ec:

    # "Somewhere I can't experience in the city,{w=.3}\nso I can feel satisfied when I leave."
    "在都市里没什么机会遇到的经验，{w=.3}\n想尽量都尝试看看，这样回去时也比较高兴。"

# game/day 6.rpy:72
translate chinese_simplified day06_ae4f12cf:

    # "...Hm?{w} I just suddenly thought of something.{w} That's\nright, {w=.3}there was something I could only do here in\nMinasato."
    "……嗯？{w}想到这里突然有什么闪了过去。{w}说起来，{w=.3}好像有什么只有在水乡这里才能做的事。"

# game/day 6.rpy:76
translate chinese_simplified day06_bd4ea703:

    # "Oh, the phone.{p}I suspend my thoughts,{w=.3}\nlazily stand up, {w=.3}and pick it up."
    "喔喔，有电话。{p}把脑中的事放到一边，{w=.3}\n懒洋洋地站了起来走到电话旁。"

# game/day 6.rpy:83
translate chinese_simplified day06_24d2332a:

    # fn "「Hello, {w=.3}[ln] speaking.」"
    fn "「你好，{w=.3}这里是西村家。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:84
translate chinese_simplified day06_46ede277:

    # ju "「...[fn]?」"
    ju "「……博行？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:85
translate chinese_simplified day06_70f30b4f:

    # "It's Juuichi-san on the other end.{p}His voice sounds lower than usual.{p}What's wrong?"
    "打电话过来的是柔一。{p}声音比平常还要低，{p}是发生什么事了吗？"

# game/day 6.rpy:86
translate chinese_simplified day06_fae18dd6:

    # fn "「Yeah, {w=.3}it's me, but...{p} Did something happen to you?」"
    fn "「是，{w=.3}是我没错……{p}柔一怎么了吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:87
translate chinese_simplified day06_1952fb49:

    # ju "「...」"
    ju "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:88
translate chinese_simplified day06_17e0c770:

    # fn "「Um, {w=.3}Juuichi-san?」"
    fn "「呃，{w=.3}柔一？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:89
translate chinese_simplified day06_577ef55e:

    # ju "「...[ln], {w=.3}there's something you've forgotten.」"
    ju "「……西村，{w=.3}你是不是有什么事忘记了？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:90
translate chinese_simplified day06_4642979f:

    # fn "「I forgot something?{p} Hmmm, {w=.3}let me think...」"
    fn "「忘了的事，{w=.3}有吗？{p}嗯，有什么事忘了吗……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:91
translate chinese_simplified day06_9434b7c9:

    # "I rack my brains trying to remember what he said I\nforgot.{w} But it wouldn't take so much effort if it was\nsomething simple."
    "被柔一这么一说，{w=.3}我就开始在脑袋里努力地回想着到底是忘记了什么事。{w}可是，要是那么容易就能想起来的话我也就不会忘记了吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:92
translate chinese_simplified day06_170c862a:

    # fn "「Maybe I did, {w=.3}but I can't think of anything...」"
    fn "「我想，{w=.3}应该是没有吧……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:93
translate chinese_simplified day06_549a3913:

    # ju "「...I see, {w=.3}so you don't remember?{p} I guess promises don't mean much to you, [ln].」"
    ju "「……是吗，{w=.3}你想不起来吗。{p}对西村来说，和别人的约定一点都不重要啊。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:94
translate chinese_simplified day06_2e8c7e34:

    # "Even though it's over the phone,{w=.3}\nI can still hear him let out a deep sigh.{p}...A promise, {w=.3}with him?"
    "虽然隔着电话，但还是感觉得出柔一深深地叹了口气。{p}……约定？{w=.3}和柔一吗？"

# game/day 6.rpy:95
translate chinese_simplified day06_d02f585f:

    # "...{p}...{p}...Oh."
    "……{p}……{p}……啊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:96
translate chinese_simplified day06_b2823954:

    # fn "「Aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaah!!」"
    fn "「啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:97
translate chinese_simplified day06_04a94896:

    # ju "「If you want to go catch fireflies again,{w=.3}\n don't bother inviting me.」"
    ju "「如果，{w=.3}你还想去看萤火虫的话，请不要找我去找别人吧。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:98
translate chinese_simplified day06_2dd1a4ae:

    # "I promised to go catch fireflies with him...!{p}How could I forget something so important?{p}I'm such an idiot!"
    "看萤火虫，已经跟柔一约好要一起去看了的……！{p}连这么重要的事竟然都能忘得干干净净，我这个大笨蛋！"

# game/day 6.rpy:99
translate chinese_simplified day06_c359a434:

    # "My cell phone doesn't work here either,\nso I can't stay in contact."
    "在这无法用手机，没有方法可以联络的水乡村里，\n所以没法保持联系。"

# game/day 6.rpy:100
translate chinese_simplified day06_554fcccf:

    # "And I can't see the river bed very well at night.{p}I kept him waiting there the whole time..."
    "而且晚上几乎看不到路的河岸旁。{p}一直让他一直在那里等着……"

# game/day 6.rpy:101
translate chinese_simplified day06_35350aec:

    # "He must have been looking all over,{w=.3}thinking something happened to me.{p}He never would have found me though."
    "因为是柔一，{w=.3}肯定会想说我该不会发生了什么事，在那附近拼命地找着吧。{p}他绝对不会找到我的。"

# game/day 6.rpy:102
translate chinese_simplified day06_328a727a:

    # "When he tried coming to my house just in case,{w=.3}\nhe saw me laughing at a variety show on tv."
    "最后因为放不下心而到我家来看看，{w=.3}\n看到的却是我在看综艺节目时发出的愚蠢笑声。"

# game/day 6.rpy:103
translate chinese_simplified day06_29d3e17a:

    # "He felt tired and disappointed when he heard me,{w=.3}\nwondering how I could so such a thing."
    "听到这个时，柔一所感受到的疲劳和失望感，{w=.3}\n到底会严重到什么程度呢。"

# game/day 6.rpy:104
translate chinese_simplified day06_38f3bc6b:

    # "I don't want to think about it,\nbut I have to.\nThis was all my fault."
    "根本不敢想象了。\n但是，却不得不去想。\n因为这全都是我的错啊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:105
translate chinese_simplified day06_3d6b6826:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san, {w=.3}I'm so sorry...」"
    fn "「柔一，{w=.3}对不起……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:106
translate chinese_simplified day06_8f1d762f:

    # ju "「...{p} It's already done.」"
    ju "「……{p}都是过去的事了。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:107
translate chinese_simplified day06_00b00233:

    # fn "「...」"
    fn "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:108
translate chinese_simplified day06_5501125c:

    # ju "「...I know you're in a festive mood because you've\n finally returned,{w=.3} but that doesn't mean you can do\n whatever you want.」"
    ju "「……你难得回来，{w=.3}\n难免做起事来会有些浮躁，这我是可以理解。{p}但是，也不能因此就做什么都没关系。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:109
translate chinese_simplified day06_a575e3b7:

    # ju "「Promises are built upon mutual trust.{p} I've known you for a long time.{p} You've never broken a promise before.」"
    ju "「约定啊，是基于对彼此的信任才能成立的东西。{p}看来我所认识的是以前的你。{p}那个不会随便打破约定的你，{w=.3}是吧。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:110
translate chinese_simplified day06_b1483277:

    # ju "「People change easily over time...{p} That's too bad.」"
    ju "「时间，竟然可以那么简单地改变一个人……{p}这真的很让人遗憾。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:111
translate chinese_simplified day06_998a3238:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san...」"
    fn "「柔一……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:112
translate chinese_simplified day06_deabf760:

    # ju "「...That's all I wanted to say.」"
    ju "「……我想说的就是这些。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:113
translate chinese_simplified day06_32094269:

    # "Without saying good-bye, {w=.3}he hangs up the phone."
    "那再见了。{w=.3}说完后他便挂上了电话。"

# game/day 6.rpy:117
translate chinese_simplified day06_c2909fbc:

    # "Click.{p}It feels like that was the sound of the path\nconnecting Juuichi-san and I closing."
    "喀嚓。{p}这声音仿佛是将我和柔一之间联系起来的通道，{w=.3}\n或者说我认为是能将我们之间联系起来的通道，给一瞬间关闭了的声音。"

# game/day 6.rpy:145
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_4b57293d:

    # "Torahiko called me over all of a sudden.{p}I wonder why?\nAnyway, I'd better get inside."
    "突然被虎彦叫出来，到底有什么事呢。{p}总之先进去吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:150
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bdcbc65e:

    # to "「Ah, [fn], you're here.{p} Tatsu-nii's coming too, so wait a bit.」"
    to "「呦～博行，来得正好。{p}辰兄也会来，稍等一下吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:151
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d956e51a:

    # fn "「So, Tatsu-nii's coming too,\n but what are we doing today?」"
    fn "「今天要去干什么呢？辰兄也会来吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:155
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9d78eb5a:

    # to "「Don't be in such a rush, I'll tell you later.{p} Hey, it looks like Tatsu-nii's right on time.」"
    to "「不用这么着急，等下就告诉你啦。{p}看。辰兄来了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:163
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_3a443026:

    # ta "「Hey, sorry to keep you waiting.{p} {nw}"
    ta "「唷，久等了。{p}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:165
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_b3eeae00:

    # ta "Oh, [fn]'s here, too?\nSo what are we doing?」"
    ta "怎么，博行也在啊，到底要干什么呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:169
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_8aa40db5:

    # to "「Now that you're both here I'll tell you.{p} You guys want to eat something tasty?」"
    to "「好，人都到齐了，告诉你们吧。{p}你们要不要来点什么好吃的呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:173
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_eeaf5cc4:

    # fn "「What are you saying all of a sudden?」"
    fn "「突然这么一说……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:177
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_486c3d4f:

    # ta "「Isn't it that?」"
    ta "「就那个吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:178
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_1976d44b:

    # ta "「The thing you always make for us?」"
    ta "「像是一直以来的那样会给俺们吃什么东西吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:179
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d8d88956:

    # fn "「'Always'?」"
    fn "「一直以来？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:183
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_f3627b23:

    # ta "「Hm? When Tora's trying out new meals,\n he gets us to taste-test for him.」"
    ta "「哦，虎做料理的时候，会让别人来试吃哦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:187
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c395a8d5:

    # to "「That's true...{p} Since I can't tell what tastes good or not,\n I need to consult someone. Usually, it's Tatsu-nii.」"
    to "「本来是这么打算的……{p}就算让辰兄帮忙试吃，无论吃什么都只会说好吃而已，没法拿来当作参考啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:191
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_25f5d878:

    # ta "「Gahaha! Whether they're good or not is no problem.{p} Because they're always good.」"
    ta "「嘎哈哈哈，俺说好吃的话不就没问题了嘛。{p}本来就很好吃的嘛」"

# game/day 6.rpy:192
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_560b44ba:

    # "This isn't much of a consultation..."
    "这样确实没法拿来当参考呢……"

# game/day 6.rpy:196
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_109203ec:

    # to "「*Cough*」"
    to "「咳咳……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:200
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_88dd4ee4:

    # to "「Eh, today we have all gathered\n to help buy the ingredients for the new\n cooking challenge that I'm doing today.」"
    to "「那个，找你们来，是因为我打算买些材料来挑战新的料理项目，所以需要你们的协助呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:204
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_05e09f14:

    # ta "「You don't really need to put on an air, do you?」"
    ta "「没必要这样郑重介绍吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:205
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_05d05ea7:

    # "Really..."
    "确实……"

# game/day 6.rpy:209
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_ff6361b4:

    # to "「Heheh. If you watched the Pururun Stay show\n on TV yesterday, it was about someone doing\n a homestay out of the country.」"
    to "「嘿嘿，昨天电视里看到的那个叫噗噜噜度假的节目，讲的是一名演员在海外寄宿家庭中的生活」"

# game/day 6.rpy:210
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_69b65c48:

    # to "「The destination was an Italian pasta maker's\n house. If you saw it, it looked so good...!{p} I had no choice, I thought 'I can make that, too.'」"
    to "「那户寄宿家庭经营着一家意大利面餐馆。光看着就觉得很好吃的样子……！{p}于是看完后，我就总想着也要这么试试」"

# game/day 6.rpy:214
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_2d3ca68a:

    # ta "「Huaaah...」{w=2}{nw}"
    ta "「哈啊～」{w=2}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:217
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bb8aaf06:

    # "Tatsu-nii, don't yawn like that.\nJust listen for a bit longer."
    "辰兄别打哈欠，仔细地听他说吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:221
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_b1080776:

    # to "「And so, because I'm making classical spaghetti,\n Tatsu-nii will go and buy the ingredients,{p} and [fn] will help.」"
    to "「所以，我要做正宗的意大利面。辰兄到街上买材料，{p}博行也一起去帮忙。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:222
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_05f10cc2:

    # to "「I've got setup to do, so you can leave me here.」"
    to "「我做准备，接下来就拜托你们啦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:226
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9def1c2b:

    # ta "「What are you saying? If we're going shopping,\n it's pointless unless you're there.{p} I'll bring the truck around, so get ready.」"
    ta "「你在说什么啊。买东西的话你不在，俺们怎么知道要买什么。{p}俺去开车过来，你们准备准备吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:234
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_32605a90:

    # to "「[fn], I'm counting on you for this.{p} I've got a list of the stuff we need.」"
    to "「博行，剩下的麻烦你了。{p}要买的材料都写在纸上了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:235
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a0dfcad7:

    # fn "「Torahiko, it should be fine if you come, too.」"
    fn "「虎彦一起去不行么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:239
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_474a35b4:

    # to "「[fn], you don't know, so it's fine,\n but Tatsu-nii's driving is freaking terrifying.{p} {nw}"
    to "「你是不知道啊，辰兄开车太恐怖了。{p}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:241
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_af547dc6:

    # extend "Just leave it at that.{w} C'mon,{w=.3} please.」"
    extend "拜托放过我吧。{w}呐，{w=.3}拜托了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:247
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_031e22b9:

    # fn "「Since this is something you want to do,\n of course you need to come too, right?」"
    fn "「因为这是自己决定要做的事，这样犹豫不决是不行的」"

# game/day 6.rpy:252
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_8aad6d50:

    # to "「Seriously.{w} I'm begging ya.」"
    to "「真的拜托啦。{w}算我求你了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:253
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e0cdf1b9:

    # fn "「Don't you think it's a bit pointless to call us\n over, then ask us to do some shopping for you?」"
    fn "「叫人家过来之后又叫人家出去买东西，不觉得这个很不合适吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:257
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_cedef90d:

    # to "「It's true I made a decision when I called you\n guys over.{w} Seems I really did get scared...{p} All right, no more thinking scary thoughts.」"
    to "「其实我在你们来的时候已经做好心理准备了，{w}可是，后来还是害怕起来……{p}不久前刚刚经历过那样的恐怖，真的不想再回忆了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:258
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_476e9f3d:

    # fn "「Is it really that bad?」"
    fn "「有那么恐怖吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:262
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_78688828:

    # to "「Really!」"
    to "「太恐怖了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:266
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c2339f5e:

    # ta "「Yo, everything's ready.」"
    ta "「喂，准备好了哦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:270
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_b23714c4:

    # to "「Damnit, this is because [fn]'s too slow!」"
    to "「可恶，都怪博行磨磨蹭蹭！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:274
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_ee92c545:

    # ta "「Tora,{w=.3} give it up.{w} In any case,\n you already said you're afraid of my driving,\n haven't you?{w} Let's just go.」"
    ta "「虎，{w=.3}别找借口了。{w}不就是，什么都没准备好吗。还说俺开车很恐怖之类的，不是吗？{w}别说那么多，出发吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:278
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_2f01d5b6:

    # to "「Ugh, damnit.\n My stomach's tying itself into knots.」"
    to "「唔，没办法了。安全带系紧点吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:279
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bd668c65:

    # "Uhh... knowing Tora's belief in letting nature\ntake its course...\nFor him to be this against it..."
    "那个，爱怎样就怎样吧，没想到虎彦\n居然害怕到这种程度……"

# game/day 6.rpy:280
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_768bac25:

    # "I'm starting to get a bad feeling about this, too."
    "不知为何，连我都感到不安了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:281
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "……"

# game/day 6.rpy:296
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e5eb0b18:

    # ta "「Okay, get in, get in.」"
    ta "「来来，上车上车」"

# game/day 6.rpy:297
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_64180602:

    # fn "「And how are we all supposed to do that?」"
    fn "「坐上去，三个人怎么坐得下？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:298
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_597c7a6b:

    # "For three people to get into a light truck,\nit seems hopeless."
    "小卡车坐三个人什么的，不觉得有点乱来么。"

# game/day 6.rpy:299
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_99a7449a:

    # "It looks barely possible, if were just Torahiko,\nwith his good physique, and Tatsu-nii."
    "光是身体壮实的虎彦和辰兄坐上去，\n就应该有点挤了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:300
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_5a54d224:

    # "Which means..."
    "话说……"

# game/day 6.rpy:301
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bf7a484a:

    # "Tatsu-nii by himself is over two metres tall,\nso how he gets in is a mystery.\nWhere's he going to ride?"
    "就算只有两米多高的辰兄去坐，\n能不能坐上去也很让人怀疑呢。\n到底要坐哪里啊？"

# game/day 6.rpy:305
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_65523391:

    # ta "「Tora,{w=.3} you can sit in the back.」"
    ta "「虎，{w=.3}你坐后面」"

# game/day 6.rpy:309
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_64d703e7:

    # to "「No way,{w=.3} absolutely not!{p} It's ok if I don't fit, I'm going home.」"
    to "「不行，{w=.3}绝对不行！{p}我受不了了，我要回去！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:313
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bfeb4630:

    # ta "「Dahaha! Kidding,{w=.3} I'm kidding.{p} We'll squeeze in.」"
    ta "「啊哈哈，开玩笑的，{w=.3}开玩笑的啦。{p}挤挤总能坐得下」"

# game/day 6.rpy:317
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_ee17320d:

    # to "「......」"
    to "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:318
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_48b0ea62:

    # to "「In that case, I'll get in first.{p} [fn], sit in between me and Tatsu-nii,\n because we might crash, you know.」"
    to "「那我先坐进去吧。{p}博行坐在我和辰兄中间，要是发生碰撞的话可就惨了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:324
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_aa3ee00e:

    # "Tatsu-nii was already sitting in the driver's seat,\nand it already looks cramped."
    "辰兄已经坐上了驾驶座，\n这样就已经十分狭窄了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:325
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_b0cb5bd9:

    # "Torahiko took the seat next to him,\nbut I'm feeling boxed in just from looking.{p}Am I really getting in like this?"
    "旁边坐着虎彦，\n光看着就感觉很挤了。{p}真的要坐上去吗？"

# game/day 6.rpy:326
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a61fe9cb:

    # fn "「Well, in I go...」"
    fn "「那么我上来了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:327
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9f8b7e75:

    # "No point in thinking.\nI forced myself into the car."
    "再怎么想也没用。\n我艰难地把身体往车里挤。"

# game/day 6.rpy:331
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_1882b2c7:

    # "On that note..."
    "说起来……"

# game/day 6.rpy:332
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_ea94a8f2:

    # "This reminds me of a show I saw once."
    "电视里有放过介绍海外的鬼畜级的内容呢。"

# game/day 6.rpy:333
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_5e3bf1d8:

    # "It was about some wagon that was full of refugees\ngetting chased by a patrol car."
    "想要非法入境的一台小型方型货车，\n被警车追上。"

# game/day 6.rpy:334
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_749a4a54:

    # "I think there were about forty people in there,\nall jammed together like baby spiders.{p}I don't think it could compare to this, though..."
    "那里面居然有40人左右，\n就像四散的人群一样跑出来的场面我看过的说。{p}和那个比起来这个算什么……"

# game/day 6.rpy:335
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_0ec7acf1:

    # ta "「Yeah, get in, come on.」"
    ta "「哦，上来上来」"

# game/day 6.rpy:340
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e668ae03:

    # to "「Oww, [fn], you're stepping on me.」"
    to "「好疼，博行，你踩到我的脚了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:341
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_17455bd5:

    # fn "「Sorry, I'll be out of the way soon.」"
    fn "「抱歉，我马上让开」"

# game/day 6.rpy:346
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_28200c24:

    # ta "「Aah,{w=.3} [fn], that's...」"
    ta "「啊，{w=.3}博行那里是……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:347
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d969e5a7:

    # fn "「Huh?{w=.3} Oh,{w=.3} sorry.」"
    fn "「唉？{w=.3}啊，{w=.3}抱歉」"

# game/day 6.rpy:348
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_60757536:

    # "I touched somewhere inappropriate, didn't I."
    "是不是碰到什么奇怪的地方了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:349
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c866fd90:

    # "But, in this place with nowhere to put my hands,\nthere's not much I can do except struggle about.\nWe're all just trying to get seats."
    "不过窄得连放手的地方都没有了，\n这种时候越是想要做什么事的话，\n只会越弄越糟吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:354
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_88ec27ed:

    # to "「[fn], your leg is in my face...」"
    to "「博行，你的脚都伸到我的脸上了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:355
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_4459ef2d:

    # fn "「Sorr...{nw}"
    fn "「抱歉……{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:360
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_6da9eba9:

    # extend "」"
    extend "」"

# game/day 6.rpy:362
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9d47731f:

    # ta "「Oooh, it's about to come out...!{p} If you keep touching it like that!!!」"
    ta "「哇，啊啊，再这样下去的话{p}会出来的！！！」「"

# game/day 6.rpy:363
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_661b059f:

    # fn "「Huh!?{w} I'm sorry!」"
    fn "「哎哎！？{w}对不起！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:368
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_66822b59:

    # to "「[fn]... your ass is in my face.{p} Is that how it is?{w} It is, isn't it.{p} Not that there's anything wrong with that.」"
    to "「博行……你的屁股都碰到我的脸了。{p}是那个吗？{w}是那个吗？{p}如果是的话我倒是不介意」"

# game/day 6.rpy:369
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_4a196b6a:

    # "I see, so I have to force myself to stand up.\nHow about this, then!!!"
    "原来如此，那样的话。\n必须要挪开！！！"

# game/day 6.rpy:374
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_7dbff243:

    # to "「Don't throw yourself onto his lap!!!」"
    to "「别睡在我膝盖上啊！！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:375
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c542148e:

    # ta "「Awesome! Do it again, harder!!!」"
    ta "「嗯，很好，就是这样，再用点力！！！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:376
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_4852518a:

    # fn "「Tatsu-nii?」"
    fn "「辰兄？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:380
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d3876426:

    # "Eventually,{w=.3} we all managed to fit in the truck."
    "最后，{w=.3}还是到翠屋组借来了大卡车。"

# game/day 6.rpy:392
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a112a68f:

    # ta "「Okay, we're here.」"
    ta "「啊，到了哦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:393
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_717ed175:

    # "We said we'd be shopping in town,\nBut the store we need is in Kazenari's outskirts..."
    "就算只是说到街上买东西，\n但商店本身已经在风鸣町的郊外了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:394
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_4bda123a:

    # fn "「Tatsu-nii, you're pretty good at driving.」"
    fn "「辰兄开的不是很好么」"

# game/day 6.rpy:395
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c78c69a5:

    # fn "「I mean, you drive way too fast,\n and there were times where we screamed,\n but nothing else really happened.」"
    fn "「虽然有时候有点过快，\n但什么事都没有啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:396
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_8ea40b1e:

    # ta "「I'm taking the Group's car, so I had to drive\n super safe. It'd be way more amazing if we took\n my light truck!」"
    ta "「今天是组里的车当然要很小心的开啦，\n俺开小卡车的话更厉害呢！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:400
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_2c663edf:

    # to "「Listen, don't ever get on Tatsu-nii's light truck.{p} If you want to survive, that is...」"
    to "「听好了，绝对不要去坐辰兄开的轻型卡车。{p}如果不想出事的话……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:404
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_6fa086fd:

    # ta "「What, you got a problem?{p} I'm not letting you ride anymore.」"
    ta "「你说什么，有意见吗？{p}下次可不会让你坐了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:408
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_cd284903:

    # to "「No, I kid, I kid.{p} You came through again, Tatsu-nii.{p} Ya saved me.」"
    to "「不，开玩笑的啦。{p}一直以来谢谢你了辰兄。{p}帮大忙了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:412
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_0c4eba71:

    # ta "「Give me a break, you're in a good mood.{p} We're here to shop, so let's get that done with.」"
    ta "「真是拿你没办法啊，你嘴真甜。{p}要买东西的话赶紧买吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:413
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c4b1366a:

    # clerk "「Welcome!」"
    clerk "「欢迎光临」"

# game/day 6.rpy:414
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_89ba06bd:

    # "Wait what, this is the import shop, World 21?"
    "哎呀，不愧是外资的商店，世界排名21。"

# game/day 6.rpy:415
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e76030af:

    # "It's bigger than I thought, and it's got more than\nfood stocked. Darts, cigarettes in colors and\nshapes I'd never seen before, antiques, toys,"
    "里面比想象的要还大，不仅有食物，\n飞镖游戏，各种看都没看过的不同牌子的香烟，\n还有古董，儿童玩具，"

# game/day 6.rpy:416
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_b7bf76cd:

    # "furniture, and more. All sorts of foreign goods\nwere lined up on the shelves.\nAn atmosphere of curiosity hung in the air."
    "连家具都有。\n各种各样的商品都摆在这里，\n到处都飘荡着鼓动人好奇心的独特气氛。"

# game/day 6.rpy:420
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c9e8662e:

    # ta "「Hey, look at this, they've got foreign minicars.{p} Foreign toys and Japanese ones are different,\n but they're kinda stylish.」"
    ta "「看看这个，外国汽车的迷你玩具哦。{p}外国的东西果然连玩具都和日本的不一样，\n感觉很时髦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:421
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_f453a9cd:

    # ta "「In Japan, there aren't any Mustang minicars.」"
    ta "「日本的话，应该是福特野马的迷你车吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:427
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_79da7b24:

    # to "「Oh, they've got portable stoves and pots, too.{p} There's also cutely shaped and efficient stuff,\n but they look hard to use.」"
    to "「哦，炉灶、锅碗之类的炊具也有卖啊。{p}样子挺可爱，还是多功能的，\n用起来好不好用呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:428
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_6ad0b433:

    # "There really is a staggering variety of things\non display."
    "真是应有尽有啊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:429
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_045c3d76:

    # fn "「It's my first time in an import goods shop,\n it's interesting to see how much stuff there is.\n It'd be hard to get bored from looking.」"
    fn "「进口杂货店我还是第一次来呢，\n有各种各样的东西真有趣。\n怎么看都不腻」"

# game/day 6.rpy:433
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_ed86f722:

    # to "「That's true. It'd be good if there was one in\n Minasato.」"
    to "「说的是啊，要是水乡村也有的话就好了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:434
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a149c215:

    # fn "「When did this one open? I wasn't around for it.」"
    fn "「我在这里的时候还没有，这个商店什么时候开业的？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:435
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_032fe7cb:

    # to "「It was finished recently, this is my first time,\n too.{w} I got interested when I heard they had\n specialty ingredients here,"
    to "「才开业没多久，我也是第一次来这里呢。{w}听说这里也有卖食材，之前还有点担心，"

# game/day 6.rpy:436
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_83ad22f1:

    # to "but it's even better than I thought.{p} I'm glad I came.」"
    to "比想象中还要好很多呢，真是来对地方了。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:440
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_4dfc731a:

    # to "「Well then, we'll buy the stuff we came for,\n go home, then I'll cook!」"
    to "「好了，材料买齐了，回去开始做吧！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:441
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_4e99dd06:

    # "Oho, he's really getting into it.{p}He get's really serious when it's time to cook.{p}I'm looking forward to when it's done."
    "哇，看起来很有信心啊。{p}虎彦做料理真是很认真呢。{p}真期待他做的料理啊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:445
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_892a5835:

    # ta "「They've got pastries over here,\n and over there it looks like they've lined up\n the sundried and canned goods.」"
    ta "「这里有点心，那边的好像是脱水蔬菜和罐头之类的东西呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:446
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_45f51edd:

    # fn "「Whoa, what's this...\n They've got whole frozen birds. Pigeon?」"
    fn "「呜啊，这个什么……整只冷冻的鸟，鸽子吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:450
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9f92b704:

    # to "「Oh yeah, they call that squab.\n It's mostly used in French cooking.」"
    to "「哦，那是山鸠，在法国料理里面经常用到」"

# game/day 6.rpy:451
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d6c64301:

    # fn "「Huh, is that so.\n Torahiko, you sure know a lot about cuisine.」"
    fn "「嘿，这样啊。虎彦对料理的事很有研究呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:455
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e707be2f:

    # to "「Uhh, yeah, kind of.」"
    to "「嗯嗯，还好啦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:456
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_347c7424:

    # "Despite Torahiko sounding triumphant as he said it,\nhe got embarrassed and red in the face afterwards."
    "虎彦刚刚还这么得意地说出来，\n之后脸有点害羞的红了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:457
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_17806e1c:

    # fn "「I see, French cuisine.{w} I don't see Tatsu-nii\n as all that French, but it feels like he could\n tear through this whole thing, right?」"
    fn "「这样啊，法国料理。{w}可是没有什么法国的感觉，辰兄他……应该不会把这个整只的生东西吧唧吧唧地吃下去吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:458
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_f308831c:

    # to "「Yeah, I get you.{w} His body's big, and his fangs\n are, too. He totally feels like a meat eater.{p} {nw}"
    to "「嗯嗯，我知道。{w}块头大，牙口好，感觉整一个肉食动物啊。{p}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:460
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bc8d9623:

    # extend "Ya beast!」"
    extend "哟～野兽！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:464
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_265582dc:

    # ta "「Just who is? I'm totally into alcohol.{p} I like Japanese style stews and fish.\n Pa talks about food a lot, so that's my influence.」"
    ta "「说谁是野兽哪？俺只是单纯喜欢酒的饮酒爱好者而已。{p}俺还喜欢煮食和鱼的日式料理，俺爹对吃可是很有讲究的」"

# game/day 6.rpy:468
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_42f43f43:

    # to "「That's funny... for a guy who likes his drink,\n you should eat just about anything,\n whether it's spicy or sweet.」"
    to "「奇怪啊……比起酒，不管甜的辣的，只要是能吃的，无论什么都吃，杂食类是这样才对啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:469
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_dfd9de93:

    # fn "「Hahaha, but Torahiko,\n earlier, didn't you say he ate meat?」"
    fn "「哈哈哈，不过虎彦你刚刚不是也说了是肉食类吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:473
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c05d3ced:

    # to "「No, you're the one who brought that up.{p} You can't judge things by their cover.」"
    to "「不，是博行提出来的吧。{p}光看外表来判断对方是不行滴」"

# game/day 6.rpy:477
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_cb601635:

    # ta "「You guys.\n How about I start at your heads,\n and tear my way through?」"
    ta "「你们！是不是想让俺把你们整只从脑袋开始吧唧吧唧地吃掉」"

# game/day 6.rpy:478
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a88ce098:

    # fn "「I'm small, and there wouldn't be much to eat...\n But if it's Tatsu-nii, then it's okay.」"
    fn "「我又小只，能吃的地方也好像没多少……不过是辰兄的话被吃掉也可以哦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:482
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_de5c9d4e:

    # to "「There's probably no place you could eat, but in\n older times people had dashi, and ate everything\n dedicated to spiritual improvement.」"
    to "「就算没多少能吃的地方，以前的人也会用鲣鱼汁设法将食物全部吃光呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:486
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_b4d00cd4:

    # to "「So I'll prepare you.{w} First, I'll cut you into\n three slabs, but you need to take off your\n clothes first. Hurry now.」"
    to "「所以就先由我来烹饪你吧。{w}要先切成三块哦，来来，把衣服脱下来」"

# game/day 6.rpy:487
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bb1e308b:

    # "I'll take my clothes off here, so please eat me."
    "我会在这个地方脱掉的，请吃掉我吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:488
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_6f302416:

    # "To be nibbled on by two people with sharp fangs\nwhile naked...{p}You,{w=.3} you beasts!!"
    "在这个地方脱的光溜溜的，被你们两个的锋利牙齿吃掉。{p}禽，{w=.3}禽兽！！"

# game/day 6.rpy:492
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_692cd950:

    # to "「What are you spacing out for?{p} Don't stand there, come over here.」"
    to "「发什么呆啊？{p}别在那种地方站着，快过来」"

# game/day 6.rpy:493
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d2ec162e:

    # "Telling me to come over after you tempted me."
    "什么啊，「过来」什么的居然由他自己来邀请。"

# game/day 6.rpy:494
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_830e72d7:

    # "I'll go, I'll go.{w} I'm going right now."
    "来了来了。{w}马上就来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:501
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_7e9cfcef:

    # ta "「Whoa,{w=.3} isn't this cartoon cheese?{p} The cheese that Jerry risked his life for,\n every day in Tom and Jerry?」"
    ta "「唔啊，{w=.3}这不是卡通奶酪嘛。{p}在《猫和老鼠》里，杰瑞每天都在拼命地找的，想要的东西吗」"

# game/day 6.rpy:502
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_bba9b7a3:

    # ta "「This is the first time I've seen it.」"
    ta "「俺还是第一次见呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:503
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e51bddb7:

    # fn "「This was also on a cooking show I saw once.{p} They fried it on top of hamburger patties.{p} It looked so good...」"
    fn "「在海蒂的家里也有过吧。{p}好像是融化后涂在面包上的。{p}看上去很好吃……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:507
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_015b33ad:

    # to "「It's Emmental cheese.」"
    to "「是瑞士多孔奶酪吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:508
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_5becca29:

    # to "「There are guys who like the smell of it,\n but the taste doesn't seem that good.」"
    to "「瑞士奶酪的香味感觉很棒，\n味道就一般般了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:509
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e4d53a64:

    # fn "「But, you want to get it so you can fry it in\n butter on hamburgers, right?」"
    fn "「不过，要是彼得的话，还会再加上那个啥一起吃……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:513
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_967aa117:

    # to "「You don't use butter for that,\n and I'm not buying cheese,\n since I'm not using it.」"
    to "「得了吧，你又不是彼得，另外，今天不用奶酪的，所以就不买了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:517
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_0cd97094:

    # ta "「Cheapass.」"
    ta "「小——气——」"

# game/day 6.rpy:518
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_86c8d1ce:

    # fn "「Stupid Kurara!{w} Buy the cheese!!」"
    fn "「克拉拉笨蛋！{w}买奶酪给我啦！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:522
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_1d4599b6:

    # to "「Tatsu-nii, don't say that.{p} Besides, you're a working adult,\n so buy it yourself.」"
    to "「辰兄，你装可爱地说话也不会可爱的。{p}话说，你都是有薪水的人了，自己买啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:523
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_377e9706:

    # ta "「For stuff like this,\n isn't it better if others buy it for you?{p} {nw}"
    ta "「这种事啊，由别人买给自己才好呢。{p}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:525
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_f1169cfa:

    # extend "Please?」"
    extend "不是吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:527
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_ffe9de37:

    # fn "「Please?」"
    fn "「不是吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:531
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_472e74a2:

    # to "「I'm already making a meal for you guys.{p} That was a mistake, wasn't it...」"
    to "「本来就是我要请你们吃东西的，\n是不是有点跑歪了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:535
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_40aa9169:

    # ta "「You can eat the cheese with some wine.{p} It's not bad having it with your food.」"
    ta "「不过，买点奶酪和葡萄酒。{p}和虎的料理一起吃也不错吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:539
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9e281a19:

    # to "「I see...\n If you want cheese so bad, we'll get this.{p} {nw}"
    to "「好吧好吧，就这么想要奶酪的话就买这个吧。{p}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:542
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_56456afe:

    # extend "C'mon, [fn].」"
    extend "给你，博行」"

# game/day 6.rpy:544
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9311fb82:

    # "Torahiko crouched down,\nand handed me a lump of cheese.{p}I didn't quite drop it, but it was really heavy."
    "虎彦蹲下把一块奶酪交给了我。{p}要是掉在地上就坏事了，所以我立刻接住，却发现它很重。"

# game/day 6.rpy:545
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_f864784e:

    # fn "「Whoa, it's heavy.{w} What is it?{p} I can't carry this unless I use both hands.{p} I don't want it at all.」"
    fn "「呜哇～好重。{w}这是什么啊？{p}不用两只手根本拿不动啊。{p}绝对不想要」"

# game/day 6.rpy:546
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_7d8230ed:

    # fn "「How're you going to use this?{w} You're buying it.{p} Man, it's so heavy...」"
    fn "「这到底要用到什么上？{w}根本用不完啊。{p}而且标价一万。唔，好重……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:550
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e16ff156:

    # ta "「Heavy, is it? I'll carry it, then.」"
    ta "「很重吗？那俺来拿吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:556
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_5b7ea049:

    # "Tatsu-nii said that,\nand then I was being lifted like a princess."
    "这么说着，辰兄把我用公主抱给抱了起来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:557
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a58091dc:

    # fn "「You're so tall, Tatsu-nii, this is how you see\n the world.{w} But... I'm holding the cheese,\n and it's seriously heavy.」"
    fn "「好高啊。辰兄一直都这样看的吗？{w}不过……奶酪仍然拿在我手里，好重的说」"

# game/day 6.rpy:558
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_31ebea32:

    # fn "「I want to stay up here, but can you put me down?」"
    fn "「虽然不舍得，但是能把我放下来么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:559
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_7661fe0c:

    # ta "「My bad, I'll put you down for now.{p} It'd be bad if you got altitude sickness.{p} Gahahaha!」"
    ta "「抱歉，这就把你放下来。{p}举得太高，把博行举出高原反应就不好了。{p}嘎哈哈哈！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:560
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_b22c3d1f:

    # to "「What's with you two. I'm getting in on this.」"
    to "「什么嘛你们，我也要加入啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:564
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_78376008:

    # "After Tatsu-nii put me down,\nTorahiko jumped onto him."
    "辰兄刚把我给放下来，虎彦就飞扑向辰兄那里去了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:565
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_11968e56:

    # "It seems his habit of pouncing\non people is still strong, huh."
    "看来虎彦喜欢飞扑向别人的习惯，\n还没改过来呢。"

# game/day 6.rpy:571
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_988854af:

    # ta "「No you don't!!」"
    ta "「太慢了！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:575
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_007b50ec:

    # "Tatsu-nii stopped Torahiko with perfect timing.\nIn one fluid movement,{p}he swept Torahiko off his feet."
    "虎彦的飞扑，被辰兄巧妙地接住了。\n并特别熟练地用公主抱抱起了虎彦。"

# game/day 6.rpy:579
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_216ac302:

    # to "「Gah.{w} You bastard, stop doing that.」"
    to "「嘁～{w}你还挺厉害的嘛」"

# game/day 6.rpy:583
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_7e4e9c0c:

    # ta "「That was naive. Who do you think you try that on\n all the time?{w} Tora, I can read your movements.{p} {nw}"
    ta "「真天真，你认为是谁每天都在被你飞扑的啊？{w}虎，你的动作我早就了如指掌了。{p}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:585
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_063bc7e5:

    # extend "You're in the palm of my hand, just like Son Goku!」"
    extend "就像手心里的孙悟空呢！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:587
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_fc17c2a6:

    # "The dragon and the tiger."
    "龙与虎。"

# game/day 6.rpy:588
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d9667bba:

    # "Each with their own powers and techniques.\nIt looks exactly like the beginning of a war.{p}The dairy corner was full of an unusual tension."
    "用各自的力量和本领冲撞着的两人，\n简直能用龙争虎斗形容的感觉。{p}乳制品专柜里，被不寻常的压迫感包围着。"

# game/day 6.rpy:589
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_8a248664:

    # "Like a princess getting argued over by two suitors,\nI could do nothing but watch."
    "被公主抱的两人，\n我只能在一旁观看。"

# game/day 6.rpy:590
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_db925152:

    # "Is there anyone capable\nof stopping this sudden fight...?"
    "这样的战斗一旦开始，\n谁都没办法阻止了吧……"

# game/day 6.rpy:591
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_0196883a:

    # clerk "「Um... excuse me.」"
    clerk "「那个……对不起」"

# game/day 6.rpy:592
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_cb0356cb:

    # clerk "「All your jumping and noisemaking is\n disturbing the other customers here.\n Could you kindly settle down, please?」"
    clerk "「你们在这里喧哗打闹，会影响到其他顾客的，请你们尽量安静地购物」"

# game/day 6.rpy:596
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_d7b6cad2:

    # ta "「Sorry.」"
    ta "「对不起」"

# game/day 6.rpy:600
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_26d2ba1d:

    # to "「Sorry.」"
    to "「对不起」"

# game/day 6.rpy:601
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_da777abb:

    # "There is!!"
    "竟然出现了！！"

# game/day 6.rpy:609
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_664a3c63:

    # ta "「We're baaack!」"
    ta "「到咯～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:613
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_8faf4b1e:

    # to "「All right, we got what we went for, time to cook!{p} I'll make it especially good, so wait here.」"
    to "「好了，该买的都买好了，开始吧！{p}绝对会做的很好吃，等一下吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:614
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9101dbc8:

    # fn "「I'm looking forward to it.{p} With all the shopping and moving around,\n my stomach is rumbling.」"
    fn "「真让人期待啊。{p}出门买了趟东西，肚子早就咕咕叫了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:618
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_c9529520:

    # ta "「I've got high hopes, Tora. No pressure.」"
    ta "「好期待啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:622
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_14aac16f:

    # to "「Don't pressure me like that.\n You're supposed to be waiting patiently for it.」"
    to "「别那么着急啦，心急吃不了热豆腐哦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:626
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_9b4aaa50:

    # "30 minutes later..."
    "30分钟后。"

# game/day 6.rpy:633
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_a6f71a37:

    # to "「Thanks for waiting, it's ready!」"
    to "「久等了，做好了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:634
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_7b0880b1:

    # fn "「This looks amazing.{p} Did you make it all yourself, Torahiko?」"
    fn "「好厉害啊。{p}这个真的都是虎彦一个人做的吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:638
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_f551617e:

    # to "「Yep.」"
    to "「当然了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:639
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e1620f7c:

    # to "「While there was some stuff I didn't have,\n I finished it off with some of my creativity.{p} I call it zucchini and tomato vegetable pasta!」"
    to "「因为用了附近买不到的材料，还融合了只有我才能创造的方法才完成的。{p}就取名为——番茄夏南瓜彩色意大利面！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:640
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_e0ba7c99:

    # "When it comes to cooking, Torahiko gets so lively.{p}Being cheerful like a kid is how he always is,\nbut it's great that he makes other people happy."
    "虎彦只要一提到料理就十分兴奋。{p}虽然平常像小孩子那样喧闹，\n但看到别人因为吃自己做的料理而高兴，也还是很赞的。"

# game/day 6.rpy:644
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_7703cce4:

    # to "「Now, hurry up and eat, before it gets cold.」"
    to "「呐，快点吃吧。{p}赶在凉掉之前」"

# game/day 6.rpy:645
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_ce294e0f:

    # fn "「Yeah, it looks good. Time to eat...!」"
    fn "「嗯，看上去很好吃啊，我不客气了～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:649
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_25219b9d:

    # ta "「This is great.」"
    ta "「这个很好吃」"

# game/day 6.rpy:651
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_17900556:

    # "*!?\n{nw}"
    "咀嚼！？{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:658
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_46fd9c61:

    # extend "This is..."
    extend "这个吧……"

# game/day 6.rpy:680
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_569474a6:

    # fn "「Awesome!!」"
    fn "「好吃～～～～～～～！！！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:685
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_849e2c1e:

    # to "「You and Tatsu-nii both think so?」"
    to "「连你也和辰兄一样啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:686
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_1e6660ea:

    # fn "「Well, that's because it's delicious.{p} That means you've got real skill, Torahiko.」"
    fn "「不是，但是真的很好吃啊。{p}就是说虎彦做料理的技巧很高的意思啦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:690
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_c21fd574:

    # to "「I see. In that case, there's more.{p} If it were just Tatsu-nii,\n he'd eat the mess-ups and still say they're good.」"
    to "「这样啊，这么说我的努力有回报了呢。{p}辰兄的话就算做得再怎么失败，他只会都说做得很好吃而已」"

# game/day 6.rpy:694
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_a19cac21:

    # ta "「If I say it's good, I mean it, Torahiko.」"
    ta "「之所以会说好吃，是因为虎彦的料理本来就好吃啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:698
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_9e2dc273:

    # to "「Hang on, you must be speaking funny.{p} [fn] said something like it, earlier.」"
    to "「那个，你说的话不觉得有点怪吗？{p}刚刚博行也说了一模一样的话呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:702
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_4ef91e45:

    # ta "「Men don't sweat the small stuff.{p} One word for tasty is enough, right?{p} Seconds!」"
    ta "「是男人就别在乎细节啦。{p}好吃一句话不就完了吗？{p}再来一碗！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:706
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_f659c32c:

    # to "「I get it.{w} Since [fn] still has some,\n you can keep stuffing yourself nonstop.」"
    to "「知道了啦。{w}博行也是，还有很多哦，\n多吃一点啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:707
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_142d8efc:

    # fn "「How about I ask for seconds, then?」"
    fn "「那，我也再来一碗」"

# game/day 6.rpy:708
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_d30e6b50:

    # ta "「Hurry up and get your own restaurant.\n Then I can eat your cooking every day.」"
    ta "「快开家自己的店子吧，好让俺们每天来蹭饭」"

# game/day 6.rpy:712
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_d693024b:

    # to "「Why does it have to be like that?{p} If I get my own store, I'm going to be using the\n Midoriya Group's truck all the time.」"
    to "「为什么要那样啊？{p}要是我有了自己的店的话，翠屋组的卡车我也要无限制免费使用」"

# game/day 6.rpy:713
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_862db387:

    # to "「You better be ready for that.」"
    to "「你们可做好心理准备」"

# game/day 6.rpy:714
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_f323ced5:

    # fn "「Hahaha! In that case, I'll also come every day\n and have you cook for me.」"
    fn "「哈哈哈，那样的话我也要在虎彦的店里，每天来蹭饭的」"

# game/day 6.rpy:718
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_8be1f7d6:

    # to "「You two are hyenas!」"
    to "「你们两个是鬣狗吗！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:722
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_f2533c2e:

    # ta "「No, I'm a dragon.」"
    ta "「并不是，在下是龙」"

# game/day 6.rpy:723
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_33bc67ce:

    # fn "「And I'm human, last I checked.」"
    fn "「在在下是人类」"

# game/day 6.rpy:727
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_b60938e9:

    # to "「Oh, whatever...{w} Just eat as much as you like.」"
    to "「算了……{w}快点吃吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:731
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_98c24b68:

    # ta "「I would, even if you didn't say anything.」"
    ta "「就算你不说俺也会把它们全部解决的」"

# game/day 6.rpy:732
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_delicious_55850db1:

    # "It really would be great,\neating Torahiko's cooking every day..."
    "要是每天都能吃到虎彦的料理该多好啊……"

# game/day 6.rpy:743
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_25219b9d:

    # ta "「This is great.」"
    ta "「这个很好吃」"

# game/day 6.rpy:744
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_53f0eedf:

    # "Tatsu-nii's eating it like it's great,\nbut I don't think it is at all..."
    "辰兄吃得好像很好吃的样子，\n但我一点也不觉得好吃……"

# game/day 6.rpy:748
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_6766539d:

    # fn "「This is badly done. I can't eat it.」"
    fn "「这个做得很失败。我没法吃」"

# game/day 6.rpy:752
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_3dcd36dd:

    # to "「...What?{p} What's badly done?{p} Just tell me!」"
    to "「……什么？{p}什么做得很失败？{p}快告诉我！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:753
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_943be7ae:

    # fn "「The sauce has good flavour,\n but it's too watery.」"
    fn "「酱汁的味道不错，但是太稀了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:754
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_22fa8181:

    # fn "「You made it right now, so you couldn't help it,\n but it needs to boil down over a long time.」"
    fn "「因为是刚做的所以没办法，\n但是需要长时间熬煮收汁才行」"

# game/day 6.rpy:755
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_08f63839:

    # fn "「The flavor is also a bit unsatisfying.{p} I think you need to add anchovies, mozzarella,\n basil, and stuff like that.」"
    fn "「味道也有点不够。{p}我觉得需要加鳀鱼、马苏里拉奶酪、\n罗勒之类的东西」"

# game/day 6.rpy:760
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_14aeb5bf:

    # to "「Guh!」"
    to "「呜！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:761
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_f89e904f:

    # fn "「The choice of noodles was perfect, but...」"
    fn "「面条的选择是完美的，但是……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:762
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_63f4fd7b:

    # fn "「The pack says 6 minutes on it,\n but you shouldn't always cook it that long.」"
    fn "「包装上写着煮6分钟，\n但不应该每次都煮那么久」"

# game/day 6.rpy:763
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_2b0a2b48:

    # fn "「Match what you make with the season,\n the temperature, the humidity... you need to vary\n the boiling time, stove heat, and amount of salt.」"
    fn "「要根据季节、温度、湿度来调整……\n煮的时间、火候、盐的用量都需要变化才行」"

# game/day 6.rpy:764
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_3b243833:

    # fn "「Then you could serve it, I think.」"
    fn "「那样的话就能端上桌了吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:765
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_11c14378:

    # fn "「You'll need to serve it beautifully.\n Pile the pasta in the middle of the plate,\n then put the sauce on top...」"
    fn "「还要摆盘摆得好看才行。\n把意大利面堆在盘子中间，\n然后把酱汁浇在上面……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:769
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_1007abbc:

    # ta "「Now that you mention it, he always makes the\n things he wants,\n but I can't think of anyone else who eats it...」"
    ta "「说起来，虎彦总是做自己想做的东西，\n但除了我们之外好像没人吃吧……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:774
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_d20b6ca8:

    # to "「Kuh!」"
    to "「呜！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:775
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_ea7d417b:

    # fn "「But, that's not all.{p} What is it, there's a faint scent...」"
    fn "「不过，还没完。{p}这是什么，有一股淡淡的味道……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:776
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_a47f93d4:

    # fn "「It's important to pay attention\n to this small thing...」"
    fn "「注意到这个细节很重要……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:777
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_6581840b:

    # fn "「In most pastas,\n the scent gives a soft, fresh taste.」"
    fn "「大多数意大利面里，\n香味能带来一种柔和清新的口感」"

# game/day 6.rpy:778
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_19805c79:

    # to "「...」"
    to "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:779
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_773e4206:

    # fn "「This sweet and sour scent... is it fruit?{p} It's not orange, not strawberry...{p} Not grape, not peach, not nashi...」"
    fn "「这个酸甜的香味……是水果吗？{p}不是橙子，不是草莓……{p}不是葡萄，不是桃子，不是梨……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:780
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_b9b63f83:

    # fn "「That's it!」"
    fn "「对了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:781
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_0f2d8316:

    # fn "「I heard in Italy, if they burn something,\n they add apples to adjust the flavour.」"
    fn "「我听说在意大利，如果煮糊了的话，\n会加苹果来调整味道」"

# game/day 6.rpy:782
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_4f32529f:

    # fn "「Because when you cook apples, in Italy,\n the taste is said to resemble tomatoes.」"
    fn "「因为在意大利，苹果煮熟后的味道，\n据说和番茄相似」"

# game/day 6.rpy:783
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_eebb251a:

    # fn "「When you made the sauce,\n you added a squeeze of apple juice.{p} You did, right?」"
    fn "「做酱汁的时候，\n你加了苹果汁对吧？{p}对吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:789
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_notgood_b368dc5d:

    # to "「...No,{w} it was ketchup.」"
    to "「……不是，{w}是番茄酱」"

# game/day 6.rpy:802
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_09f1e858:

    # "What do I do...?"
    "怎么办才好……？"

# game/day 6.rpy:803
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_c3823000:

    # "I don't really like spaghetti.{p}Or tomatoes, for that matter..."
    "我其实不太喜欢意大利面。{p}或者说，不太喜欢番茄……"

# game/day 6.rpy:804
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_abcd4535:

    # "But, I can't just say I hate it."
    "但是，不能直接说讨厌。"

# game/day 6.rpy:805
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_f0a6c5e2:

    # "Maybe I can bluff my way through this."
    "也许可以蒙混过关。"

# game/day 6.rpy:806
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_9fd0ef89:

    # fn "「Whoa, it's good.」"
    fn "「哇，好吃」"

# game/day 6.rpy:810
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_c59288e4:

    # ta "「Tasty tasty.」"
    ta "「好吃好吃」"

# game/day 6.rpy:814
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_240a7a0f:

    # to "「I see... if you don't want seconds, just tell me.」"
    to "「是吗……不想吃第二碗的话，直说就好」"

# game/day 6.rpy:818
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_8ab235e1:

    # "Damn...{p}That was a little cold.{p}Well, I'll leave the seconds to Tatsu-nii."
    "糟糕……{p}那句话有点冷淡。{p}算了，第二碗就留给辰兄吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:822
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_cb94db57:

    # ta "「Phew, I ate so much.{w} Such good food and wine.{p} It was a good plan to do wine and cheese,\n after all.{w} {nw}"
    ta "「呼，吃饱了。{w}这么好的菜和葡萄酒。{p}果然买了葡萄酒和奶酪之后配着吃是正确的。{w}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:824
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_43ffc3e9:

    # extend "Okay, next is dessert.」"
    extend "好，接下来是甜点」"

# game/day 6.rpy:828
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_bd874e6f:

    # fn "「Wai-{w=.3}what are you doing, stop it.{p} I told you not to touch me there, Tatsu-nii.」"
    fn "「等——{w=.3}你在做什么，住手。{p}我不是说过不要摸那里吗，辰兄」"

# game/day 6.rpy:833
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_c083b178:

    # ta "「C'mon, it's fine...!」"
    ta "「来嘛，没事的……！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:834
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_71551ed8:

    # ta "「Today, when I almost came out,\n weren't you touching me?」"
    ta "「今天在车里的时候，\n不是你摸了我吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:838
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_b4b212e7:

    # ta "「That gorgonzola I ate earlier,\n it stank real bad,\n but what would you smell there?」"
    ta "「我之前吃的那块戈尔根佐拉奶酪，\n臭得要命，\n但你那里会是什么味道呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:839
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_4a5fc6ff:

    # "Tatsu-nii pinned me to his body, touched me here,\nthere, and all over, licked the back of my neck,{p}and generally sexually harrassed me."
    "辰兄把我按在身上，这里那里到处摸，\n舔我的后颈，{p}简直就是在性骚扰。"

# game/day 6.rpy:840
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_e1ecf105:

    # "Drinking habits are really bad.{p}It feels a little exciting,\nbut it's still really bad."
    "酒品真差。{p}感觉有点小兴奋，\n但还是真的很差。"

# game/day 6.rpy:841
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_f4dcf92f:

    # fn "「It's bad, Tatsu-nii.{w} I won't eat it.」"
    fn "「不行，辰兄。{w}我不吃了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:845
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_5ca5b9e6:

    # to "「It was bad, huh...{p} My bad for making something inedible.」"
    to "「很难吃吧……{p}对不起，做了没法吃的东西」"

# game/day 6.rpy:846
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_ea0bd000:

    # fn "「That's wrong. It's not that, Tora, Tatsu-nii...」"
    fn "「不是那样的，虎彦，辰兄他……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:850
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_beaab1f3:

    # to "「Sorry, Tatsu-nii was a bust, too...{p} Don't force yourself to eat it.{p} Send the plate back, I'll clean up.」"
    to "「抱歉，辰兄也算了……{p}不要勉强自己吃了。{p}把盘子收回来吧，我来收拾」"

# game/day 6.rpy:851
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_fd2daaec:

    # fn "「Wait, that's not it, Tatsu-nii's-」"
    fn "「等等，不是那样的，辰兄他——」"

# game/day 6.rpy:855
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_26fbd801:

    # ta "「You wait, too. You wanna touch, don't you?{p} Come over here. You can tie me up if you want.」"
    ta "「你也等着。你想摸对吧？{p}过来这边。你想把我绑起来也可以哦」"

# game/day 6.rpy:856
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_9968c478:

    # fn "「Ahh!」"
    fn "「啊！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:857
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_077b390a:

    # "I give up."
    "我放弃了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:858
translate chinese_simplified torahiko06_disgusting_ee9eb320:

    # "I've been misunderstood,\nbut I wonder if I could persuade him..."
    "虽然被误解了，\n但也许能说服他……"

# game/day 6.rpy:875
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_b4f606a7:

    # "「Thank you very much!」"
    "「谢谢惠顾～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:876
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_190b8edc:

    # "With ice cream in one hand,{p}I leave the candy store."
    "单手拿着雪糕，{p}走出了糖果店。"

# game/day 6.rpy:877
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_cc2d0bc6:

    # "Again I meet the horrible humidity and sun.{p}The weather today is a little too good..."
    "再次来到蒸笼一般闷热的空气中。{p}水乡村今天依旧是个好得过分的天气。"

# game/day 6.rpy:878
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_e1b67c42:

    # fn "「It's so hot...」"
    fn "「好热啊……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:879
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_800d91f2:

    # "I just bought this ice cream soda,{p}and it's already melting and dripping.{p}That was quick."
    "刚刚买来的雪糕，{p}已经开始融化了，{p}我可不想这样。"

# game/day 6.rpy:880
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_57c6ddd1:

    # "Hiding in the shade of the storefront,{p}I eat my ice cream,{p}and flap my shirt with my left hand."
    "躲到店子的阴影里，{p}我吃着雪糕，{p}用左手啪嗒啪嗒地掀着衣服扇风。"

# game/day 6.rpy:881
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_9a72fb89:

    # who "「Hey, [fn]!」"
    who "「喂——博行～！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:882
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_96ebc8ac:

    # "From across the road,{p}somebody waves their hand,{p}and comes this way."
    "道路的对面，{p}有个人正一边挥手，{p}一边朝这边走来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:883
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_dde83c31:

    # "That's..."
    "那是……"

# game/day 6.rpy:884
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_1fc50344:

    # fn "「Kounosuke?」"
    fn "「孝之助？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:889
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_fd6a6670:

    # ko "「Whew, I finally found you!」"
    ko "「哈啊，总算是找到了。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:890
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_2764f289:

    # "In this awful heat,{p}you'll sweat just from standing.{p}You can imagine what'd be like if you ran."
    "这么热的天，{p}光是站着就已经汗流浃背了，{p}用跑的话更是不堪想象。"

# game/day 6.rpy:891
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_a256af2b:

    # "Kounosuke's shirt sticks to his body.{p}It's soaked through with sweat.{p}He puts his hands on his knees and pants."
    "孝之助的衬衫紧贴在身上，{p}被汗水湿透了，{p}双手撑着膝盖不停喘着气。"

# game/day 6.rpy:892
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_540ce0ef:

    # fn "「What's wrong? You're out of breath.」"
    fn "「怎么了？上气不接下气的。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:893
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_f7a492c6:

    # ko "「Huh? It's not a big deal...」"
    ko "「唔，不不，并不是什么大事啦。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:897
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_1ac8ede5:

    # ko "「Ah, that ice cream looks good!」"
    ko "「啊，雪糕，真好啊。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:898
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_076b5471:

    # fn "「You can't have it.」"
    fn "「不会给你吃哦。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:902
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_086b0851:

    # ko "「Tightwad.」"
    ko "「小气～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:903
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_3d1f5c1a:

    # fn "「Go get some yourself.{p} Anyways, what do you want?」"
    fn "「想吃自己去买。{p}话说，有什么事吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:904
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_880a50c1:

    # "I steer the dicussion back on track.{p}Kounosuke remembers what he came to me for,{p}and claps his hands together."
    "我将跑偏的话题拉回正轨。{p}孝之助想起了来找我有什么事，{p}「啪」地拍了一下手。"

# game/day 6.rpy:908
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_3791fd37:

    # ko "「Ah, that's right.{p} This evening, around 7 or 8,{p} could you meet me in front of the school?」"
    ko "「啊，对了对了。{p}今天晚上，七、八点左右的时候，去不去学校那边集合？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:909
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_37de9256:

    # fn "「Why?」"
    fn "「干什么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:913
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_9e72bbbd:

    # ko "「I'm planning a test of courage!」"
    ko "「我想搞个试胆大会。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:914
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_cd1f6cd2:

    # fn "「A test of courage...?」"
    fn "「试胆大会……？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:918
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_11272262:

    # ko "「Yep. You know it's been so hot lately,{p} I figured this would be a good time to do it.」"
    ko "「嗯。你看，最近不是热得很嘛，{p}这不正好～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:919
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_66964245:

    # "A test of courage, huh..."
    "试胆大会啊……"

# game/day 6.rpy:920
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_4176cf47:

    # ko "「It would be great with just 1 or 2 people.{p} Pleeeaaase!?」"
    ko "「只有一两人才不够办试胆大会的。{p}拜托了！？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:921
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_8668fb87:

    # "As he says that,{p}Kounosuke puts both hands together,{p}and bows his head."
    "孝之助一边说着，{p}双手合十，{p}低下了头。"

# game/day 6.rpy:922
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke06_0622b9c9:

    # "Indifferent to Kounosuke's preface, I..."
    "对这般没有长篇大论的孝之助式请求，我……"

# game/day 6.rpy:937
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_e49e71f0:

    # fn "「There's nothing to worry about?」"
    fn "「倒是没什么关系啦。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:938
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_9b41fca8:

    # "I had no reason to refuse the offer,{p}so I agreed to go."
    "也没有什么拒绝的理由，所以就这样答应下来了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:942
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_4d472376:

    # ko "「Thank you [fn]!!」"
    ko "「谢谢你啊，博行～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:943
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_b9ac9151:

    # "With that, he tightly grasps my left hand,{p}and with all of his strength,{p}he shakes it up and down."
    "一边说着，孝之助一边握住我空着的那只手，{p}大力地上下摇动着。"

# game/day 6.rpy:944
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_196afbb8:

    # fn "「Hey, I dropped my ice cream!」"
    fn "哎呀，雪糕要掉下来了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:948
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_981683e2:

    # ko "「Aah, sorry!」"
    ko "「啊啊，抱歉。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:949
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_cdbf0b20:

    # fn "「Jeez...」"
    fn "「真是的。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:950
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_ddf2efb9:

    # "He says that just as restless as ever,{p}but really he's over reacting."
    "和以前一样，不知道该不该说是不够冷静，{p}总之反应还是这般夸张。"

# game/day 6.rpy:954
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_1c1445c9:

    # ko "「But with this,{p} I've gathered a number of people.{p} I'm really thankful, [fn]!」"
    ko "「这样的话，人数终于凑齐了～。{p}真是太谢谢了，博行」"

# game/day 6.rpy:958
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_76137c00:

    # ko "「Alright then.{p} Tonight, don't forget!」"
    ko "「那，等会儿见哦～。{p}今天晚上，不要忘喽～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:959
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_8074338a:

    # fn "「Yeah.」"
    fn "「嗯ー」"

# game/day 6.rpy:960
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_dc499a8f:

    # "Right as he's finished talking,{p}he runs off in the opposite direction he came.{p}What a busy guy..."
    "说完之后，{p}孝之助向着来时的反方向跑开了。{p}真是忙碌的家伙呢。"

# game/day 6.rpy:961
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_966bf424:

    # "Really, Kounosuke was carefree back then,{p}but he was acting so restlessly,{p}usually..."
    "真是的，孝之助从以前的时候开始，{p}就一直这样咋咋乎乎的，{p}一直都……。"

# game/day 6.rpy:962
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_eddd4463:

    # "(Usually...?)"
    "（一直都……？）"

# game/day 6.rpy:963
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_38a5dfe1:

    # "As I was thinking to myself,{p}an alarm goes off in my head.{p}An alarm that's been dormant for 5 years."
    "由于五年的空白期，{p}一不小心就把我思考回路上的按钮给关上了，{p}到现在才突然响起警报来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:964
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_d01776f8:

    # "For Kounosuke to talk like that suddenly,{p}means he has some good-for-nothing plan..."
    "孝之助一直以来，像那样地提出些什么的时候，{p}最后都会发生不好的事情……"

# game/day 6.rpy:965
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_ebffd867:

    # "Well, I know he doesn't mean any harm,{p}but..."
    "虽然知道孝之助本人并没有恶意，{p}但是……"

# game/day 6.rpy:966
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_2d3f991f:

    # "But his tendencies to get in trouble,{p}and his weird curiousities,{p}make him a nuisance sometimes..."
    "不过，就因为想奉陪到底的好奇心，最后被卷入大麻烦的话，{p}那才是真正的大麻烦。"

# game/day 6.rpy:967
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_90182dc8:

    # "I mean, he really is a good guy,{p}so he has no bad intent."
    "这种状况，{p}相比起他的无意之恶，倒才算是真正的灾难。"

# game/day 6.rpy:968
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_d5bbaa37:

    # "(I wouldn't say it's strange, would I...?)"
    "（该不会又提出一些奇怪的事情吧……？）"

# game/day 6.rpy:969
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_993a812c:

    # "Now I'm starting to get excited and anxious,{p}and I feel the midsummer air around my body."
    "带着姗姗来迟的不安，{p}盛夏的闷热空气吹拂着我的身体。"

# game/day 6.rpy:970
translate chinese_simplified day06_accepttest_667f1693:

    # "I hope this isn't anything weird,{p}but I wonder..."
    "但愿最终不要演变成什么奇怪的事件……"

# game/day 6.rpy:979
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_676ca5b8:

    # fn "「Sorry, I don't think today will work...」"
    fn "「抱歉，今天有些事。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:983
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_e2842ad6:

    # ko "「Eh!?」"
    ko "「诶——」"

# game/day 6.rpy:984
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_5312fbe0:

    # fn "「Look, I'm really sorry!{p}How about another time?」"
    fn "「抱歉，能不能下次再去？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:988
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_5d92427d:

    # ko "「Are you absolutely sure you don't want to?」"
    ko "「无论怎样都不行吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:989
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_20fd7668:

    # fn "「I'm sure.」"
    fn "「没办法啊。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:993
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_6f7b1ba4:

    # ko "「I see... yeah.{p}Some other time, then.」"
    ko "「这样啊……那，下次再说吧。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:997
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_8d526603:

    # "Kounosuke's dropping shoulders make me feel...{p}guilty."
    "看着垂头丧气的孝之助，我的心里隐隐作痛……"

# game/day 6.rpy:998
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_7a220db1:

    # "Actually, I have no plans tonight...{p}but wait a minute!"
    "其实我并没有什么要紧的事情要做。{p}不过！"

# game/day 6.rpy:999
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_3a1da643:

    # "Usually when Kounosuke's like that,{p}he's probably trying to get me involved.{p}Involved with something that's no good!"
    "孝之助一般提议起什么事情的时候，{p}基本上都会被卷入什么大麻烦之中。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1000
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_773769c8:

    # "Kounsouke usually doesn't mean any harm,{p}but it's hard to tell this time."
    "虽然说孝之助本人并没有恶意，{p}但是必须把这种状况也考虑进去才行。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1001
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_e78d7339:

    # "I just walk back into the candy store.{p}I feel a little sorry.{p}But that's about it."
    "虽然看着慢慢地挪进糖果屋的孝之助的背影有些可怜，{p}但是……{p}这是两码事。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1002
translate chinese_simplified day06_declinetest_2ac5cf9e:

    # "(I guess it's a little late...{p}to not be cold to him, he's a nice guy.)"
    "（如果不是总迟到的话，倒是个挺不错的家伙吧。）"

# game/day 6.rpy:1014
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_6a7b4cb8:

    # "A little past 7:00 PM."
    "刚过了下午7点。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1015
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_1f99e842:

    # "Being wrapped in the light of dusk,{p}the atmosphere feels kind of lonely."
    "附近已被笼罩在淡淡的黑暗中，{p}连空气也变得安静起来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1016
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_59997208:

    # "As told by Kounosuke,{p}I'm in front of the school.{p}There's Torahiko and Shun."
    "我按照孝之助说的，来到了学校前。{p}在那儿——"

# game/day 6.rpy:1022
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_788b483d:

    # to "「Oh, [fn]!」"
    to "「嗨，博行！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1026
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_7dd955d9:

    # su "「Ah, [fn]-san. Good evening!」"
    su "「啊，博行晚上好呀～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1027
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_d541216c:

    # "Kounosuke mentioned two other people coming,{p}this must be who he meant."
    "虎彦和峻已经到了呢。{p}大概这两个也是孝之助叫来的试胆成员吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1028
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_81347085:

    # fn "「Huh? Just two people?」"
    fn "「咦？只有你们两个人？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1032
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_2b7b3938:

    # su "「Yep.」"
    su "「是啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1033
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_b5661310:

    # fn "「And Kounosuke?」"
    fn "「孝之助人呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1037
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_26e330ee:

    # to "「Not here yet.」"
    to "「还没来……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1038
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_cb2f32cf:

    # fn "「......」"
    fn "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1040
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_41d5f799:

    # to "「Jeez, he's the one who told us to come,{p} and of course he has to be here late...」"
    to "「真是的，{p}他自己怎么还迟到了呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1041
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_3e8602da:

    # "He hasn't made any progress at all..."
    "一点进步都没有……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1042
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_731cd116:

    # "He's in high school already.{p}I thought he'd be a little better by now,{p}but..."
    "还以为他进入高中了，{p}能稍微强一点了呢，{p}不过……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1043
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_d4b8326a:

    # fn "「His habit of being late...{p} he still hasn't gotten rid of it...」"
    fn "「孝之助爱迟到的毛病……{p}还是没治好呀……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1047
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_db171ddf:

    # to "「He's never going to get rid of it.」"
    to "「大概一辈子都治不好了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1048
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_51270daa:

    # "Well, it's what I expected...{p}But it is Kounosuke. Hmm."
    "不，应该不会那样……{p}不过孝之助吗……嗯……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1049
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_33ce39e9:

    # "Should I say I'm impressed,{p}or should I just give up?{p}This mood makes me put my hand to my head."
    "我也不知该说是佩服，{p}还是该放弃呢。{p}这种心情让我不禁抱住了头。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1053
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_6ea60c11:

    # su "「B-but I'm getting kind of nervous.{p} We're meeting at a time like this...」"
    su "「但、但是这个时间集合，{p}还真让人有点紧张呢」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1054
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_ac996258:

    # "To cover up for Kounosuke,{p}Shun-kun hastily changes the topic.{p}Wait, Shun-kun?"
    "峻说出了让人心慌的话题，这不正符合孝之助的计划么。{p}话说，峻君？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1055
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_af647853:

    # fn "「Huh?{p} Don't you have a curfew?{p} Is this going to be alright?」"
    fn "「对了，{p}峻这么晚回家没问题吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1059
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_e6968b7b:

    # su "「Oh, yeah!{p} My mom gave me permission.{p} No big deal.」"
    su "「嗯，是的！{p}今天苦苦地向母亲哀求，终于得到了许可，没问题了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1060
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_b4799822:

    # fn "「Hmm...」"
    fn "「哦……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1061
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_3b16f17e:

    # "I'd say he's breaking his curfew,{p}so he can go out and play at this time.{p}I guess this tickled his childish curiousity..."
    "他一定是违反门禁，{p}才能在这个时间跑出来玩。{p}一定是被他孩子般的好奇心驱使了吧……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1062
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_4d450086:

    # "They're waiting in a similar way,{p}except Torahiko's getting frustrated,{p}while Shun-kun seems to be somewhat cheerful."
    "同样是在等，{p}和焦躁的虎彦不同，{p}峻君倒是显得喜不自禁。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1066
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_e6ac77b9:

    # to "「Nevertheless, Kounosuke is such a slow guy.」"
    to "「话虽这么说，孝之助那家伙也太慢了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1072
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_9b4aaa50:

    # "30 minutes later..."
    "30分钟后——"

# game/day 6.rpy:1082
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_e1ae7f0b:

    # ko "「You kept me waiting!」"
    ko "「大家久等了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1083
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_218839c4:

    # "By now, it had become darker.{p}Finally, the expedition leader shows up..."
    "几乎周围全都暗下来的时候，{p}主办者大人终于出现了……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1087
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_b6303022:

    # fntora "{size=+50}『You're late. 』"
    fntora "{size=+50}『好晚！』"

# game/day 6.rpy:1091
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_4760b1e8:

    # ko "「But I spent so much time preparing!」"
    ko "「因为我要花时间准备嘛……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1095
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_cfbc0990:

    # to "「Even though you're the one who told us,{p} \"not to be late.\"」"
    to "「说得倒挺好，{p}自己组织的竟然还迟到！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1099
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_334484cb:

    # ko "「What!? I'm not late.{p} I told you to be here at 7 or 8,{p} didn't I?」"
    ko "「啊？哪有迟到。{p}说好了不是7点到8点嘛……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1105
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_721b8915:

    # everybody "「......」"
    everybody "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1106
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_23834224:

    # "Kounosuke says that incorrigibly,{p}and puts it aside."
    "孝之助毫无愧疚之意地说。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1110
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_1ceeec14:

    # to "「I'm going home...」"
    to "「我要回去了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1114
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_3c769d87:

    # ko "「Wha!? I'm sorry I made you wait,{p} Torahiko!」"
    ko "「哎！？对不起让你们久等了，{p}虎彦！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1115
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_c47e75a9:

    # to "「If that's what you really think,{p} then you can start by making an honest apology.」"
    to "「要是真的这么想的话，{p}就要诚恳地道歉！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1119
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_ab9a9dcf:

    # ko "「Y-yes, I'll reflect on this...」"
    ko "「是、是，我会反省的……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1120
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_5853a8bb:

    # "Ah, I've missed this.{p}The comedy of Kounosuke and Torahiko."
    "好怀念啊，{p}孝之助和虎彦的对口相声。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1124
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_05986b2c:

    # to "「Alright then, what have you been planning?{p} You even called Shun out for this!」"
    to "「那……你打算做什么呢？{p}连峻都叫出来了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1125
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_340fbb3c:

    # fn "「Isn't this a test of courage?」"
    fn "「做什么？当然是试胆了吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1129
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_9ddc062a:

    # to "「Coura...!?」"
    to "「试、试胆……！？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1133
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_12511176:

    # ko "「Well, it's Summer, it's night,{p} and we're at the school, right?」"
    ko "「那个，在夏天，{p}在夜里，又在学校，{p}要做的只有一件事了吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1134
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_14a1bc31:

    # "Then, Kounosuke's takes out a flashlight.{p}With a click of the switch,{p}he turns it on."
    "说着，孝之助从包里取出了手电筒。{p}『啪』的一声打开了开关。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1140
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_31fa096d:

    # ko "「Therefore...{p} this is now the,{p} \"Seven Wonders of Minasato School\" challenge."
    ko "「就是这么回事……{p}接下来，{p}『水乡学校七大不可思议』挑战赛——」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1141
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_e4020139:

    # ko "I would like to hold a competition.{p} A test of courage competition!」"
    ko "「试胆大会！{p}正式开始！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1142
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_cd917897:

    # "Getting himself psyched up,{p}Kounosuke begins to explain the rules."
    "孝之助自顾自地开始说明规则。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1143
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_a1f7c37d:

    # "We're to be divided into 2 teams of 2 pairs,{p}for every one of the Seven Wonders you find,{p}you get 3 points."
    "两个人一组分成两队，{p}每找到一个七大不可思议的地点，{p}就得3分。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1144
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_b7ea3f0f:

    # "As proof of that,{p}you must take a picture at each location.{p}It's something like that."
    "在每个到过的地方拍照，证明你到过那里。{p}大概就是这么一回事。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1145
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_aa493787:

    # "For the sake of developing photos,{p}this seems like a good chance,{p}to take a lot of photos..."
    "附带一提，{p}为了拍出好照片，{p}途中拍多少张都可以。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1146
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_cc615a4b:

    # ko "「To not use all of the film,{p} would be a shame, wouldn't it?」"
    ko "「不好好用光胶卷的话，{p}太可惜了嘛？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1150
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_c33023c5:

    # to "「W-wait a minute,{p} did I not hear that correctly!?」"
    to "「等……等一下，{p}我怎么没听说有这事！？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1154
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_e3ba185f:

    # ko "「Huh? Ah, sorry.{p} Did I forget to say something?」"
    ko "「嗯？啊，抱歉。{p}我忘记说了吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1158
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_bbce318e:

    # to "「On the pictures,{p} what if something... err...{p} strange shows up on one!?」"
    to "「另外，{p}要是照片里拍到了奇怪的东西{p}该怎么办！？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1162
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_06ac6f1c:

    # ko "「I'm not expecting that.」"
    ko "「那正是我所希望的啊」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1163
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_0e2ffacc:

    # ko "「Still, I'd like to take one myself...{p} a ghost photograph...」"
    ko "「果然，{p}哪怕只有一次也好，让我亲手拍到灵异照片……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1164
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_0fd4d656:

    # "......"
    "……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1165
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_28bf886f:

    # "Kounosuke sounds so indifferent...{p}Everybody else is lost for words,{p}not just Torahiko."
    "孝之助说得那么满不在乎……{p}不光是虎彦，在场的所有人都无语了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1166
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_b003b663:

    # "Oh... I see."
    "啊——原来是这样。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1167
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_715ab098:

    # fn "「In other words...{p} this test of courage is just so...{p} you can take ghost photos...?」"
    fn "「也就是说……{p}这次试胆的真正目的，{p}是为了拍到灵异照片吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1171
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_0aaf8b54:

    # ko "「Yes.」"
    ko "「ye~~~s」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1172
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_9d6656c6:

    # "Just like always,{p}he can't come up with anything good."
    "真是的，{p}一如既往地没有像样的思考呢。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1176
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_3695fe1f:

    # to "「I-I... I don't want anything...{p} to do with this crap!!」"
    to "「我……我才不想……{p}跟这种无聊的事扯上关系！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1177
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_5fae2140:

    # fn "「Oh, why not?」"
    fn "「嘛，不是挺有趣的么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1181
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_3bc91385:

    # to "「[fn]? You too...?」"
    to "「博行？你也是……？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1182
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_ee25e5f5:

    # fn "「Ghost photography aside,{p} I'll just consider this...{p} a normal test of courage."
    fn "「灵异照片暂且不提，{p}只当作普通的试胆不就行了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1183
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_aa9f12a6:

    # fn "Besides, this is nostalgic.」"
    fn "而且这多令人怀念呀。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1184
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_9ca0b450:

    # "In this old fashioned building,{p}is where we used to go to school."
    "这老旧的木质校舍，{p}是我们曾经上学的地方。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1188
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_a0d58c6b:

    # ko "「As expected of [fn].{p} Being open-minded!」"
    ko "「不愧是博行！{p}心真宽！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1189
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_6ee423c3:

    # "Just like always,{p}Kounosuke's the only excited one..."
    "依然是孝之助一个人热情高涨。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1190
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_68167d8b:

    # "He goes on and on,{p}about what he was talking about earlier."
    "他滔滔不绝地，{p}继续说着之前的话题。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1191
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_fb968a21:

    # "He still hasn't convinced Torahiko,{p}but as Kounosuke goes on,{p}Torahiko realizes that it's useless to resist."
    "虽然还没说服虎彦，{p}但看着孝之助继续说下去，{p}虎彦也意识到反对是没用的了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1192
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_16698e35:

    # "He stays silent."
    "他沉默了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1199
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_2dc93fb2:

    # "And Shun-kun...{p}He's been silent for a while,{p}but it seems like..."
    "再看峻君……{p}从刚才开始就什么也没说，{p}一直在认真地听……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1200
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_b9eb832b:

    # "He's taking Kounosuke pretty seriously."
    "好像一直在认真地听着孝之助的话。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1206
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_cfce1dbb:

    # ko "「Well then,{p} let's decide how to split up...」"
    ko "「嗯——{p}差不多该决定怎么分组了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1207
translate chinese_simplified day06_testofcourage_e9307243:

    # "Now, what should I do?"
    "那，我该怎么选呢？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1222
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_kounosuke_b4692015:

    # fn "「Alright then...{p} I'll go with Kounosuke.」"
    fn "「那么……{p}我和孝之助一组。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1223
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_kounosuke_8352824f:

    # "Kounosuke is still out of control,{p}I'll go with him to keep an eye on him."
    "还是担心孝之助暴走，{p}和他一组还能监视一下他。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1227
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_kounosuke_d07e635c:

    # "The places we're going to are the library,{p}the gym, and the art room."
    "我们要去的地方有图书室、{p}体育馆，还有图工室。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1242
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_torahiko_dc6a8487:

    # fn "「Alright then...{p} I'll go with Torahiko.」"
    fn "「那么……{p}我和虎彦一组。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1243
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_torahiko_7f137f84:

    # "Torahiko seems to be the most reliable,{p}so I choose him."
    "虎彦最可靠了，{p}所以我选他。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1247
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_torahiko_494795fb:

    # "We're told to go to the gym,{p}the stairs, and the music room."
    "我们要去的地方有体育馆、{p}楼梯，还有音乐教室。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1262
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_shun_d0868e34:

    # fn "「Alright then...{p} I'll go with Shun-kun.」"
    fn "「那么……{p}我和峻君一组。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1263
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_shun_59cbb7d8:

    # "Of all of us here,{p}he's the youngest,{p}so I need to take care of him."
    "这些人里他最年轻，{p}我必须好好照顾他。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1264
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_shun_c2eda981:

    # "Who knows what would happen,{p}if I left him with Kounosuke or Torahiko."
    "不知道把他交给孝之助或虎彦会怎样。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1268
translate chinese_simplified day06_pick_shun_650fb7bf:

    # "The places we're supposed to go are the stairs,{p}the library, and the science room."
    "我们要去的地方有楼梯、{p}图书室，还有理科室。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1283
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_ff91208f:

    # su "「Excuse me, may I say something?」"
    su "「那个，能稍微问一下吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1287
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_0c786c86:

    # ko "「Sure Shun-kun.{p} What is it?」"
    ko "「好的峻君。{p}怎么了？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1291
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_6333aae5:

    # su "「It's Minasato School's \"Seven\" Wonders.{p} Isn't that one too many?」"
    su "「不是说水乡学校有七大不可思议么？{p}不是还差一个么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1292
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_8259c592:

    # fn "「Oh, that's right.」"
    fn "「啊啊，那个啊。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1293
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_3b4abd01:

    # "I answer instead of Kounosuke."
    "我代替孝之助回答了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1294
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_645425ac:

    # fn "「They say that,{p} when you know what the seventh wonder is,{p} something strange will happen.」"
    fn "「据说，{p}当你知道了第七个不可思议是什么的时候，{p}就会发生怪异的事情。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1295
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_6fe4ae39:

    # fn "「Nobody knows what the seventh wonder is,{p} even I have absolutely no idea.」"
    fn "「所以第七个不可思议谁也不知道，{p}就算知道了也绝对不能告诉别人。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1296
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_e700b5b9:

    # "I lower my tone,{p}to make it sound a little eerie."
    "我压低了音调，{p}想说得更有恐怖气氛一些。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1297
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_aab9a946:

    # "A lukewarm, nighttime Summer breeze,{p}caresses my cheek."
    "夏天暖暖的夜风，{p}吹拂着脸颊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1298
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_2d5892b5:

    # "The mood should have been perfect,{p}but it didn't seem to do much for Shun-kun."
    "虽然气氛制造得很到位，{p}但峻君看起来似乎没受什么影响。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1299
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_db4974ef:

    # "He has a blank look on his face,{p}while I become more awkward."
    "他一脸茫然，{p}反倒是让我变得有些尴尬了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1300
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_918b7a97:

    # fn "「Th-the point is...{p} now you should be excited,{p} to see the seventh wonder!」"
    fn "「那、那个……{p}你们应该对第七个不可思议，{p}更有期待才对！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1304
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_21620e98:

    # su "「Huh?」"
    su "「哎？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1305
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_e9279d7c:

    # fn "「In other words,{p} the seventh wonder is a ghost story."
    fn "「也就是说，{p}第七个不可思议就是一个怪谈。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1306
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_ef2071fd:

    # fn "「A \"secret you're not supposed to know\",{p} kind of thing.{p} The rumor itself is a ghost story.」"
    fn "「所谓的『不能知道的秘密』，{p}就是这种东西。{p}传言本身就是怪谈了。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1310
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_82ed2899:

    # su "「Oh, I see!」"
    su "「啊啊，原来如此！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1311
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_9138eba6:

    # "In understanding,{p}Shun-kun's ears stand on end."
    "理解之后，峻君的耳朵竖了起来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1312
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_a977362d:

    # "His tail sways gently behind him.{p}Oh, he's so cute..."
    "身后的尾巴轻轻摇着。{p}真是太可爱了……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1315
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_975534c0:

    # ko "「[fn], that's not right...」"
    ko "「博行，不是那样的……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1316
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_b5ad05af:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    fn "「哎？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1317
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_c714af10:

    # ko "「Of the Seven Wonders of Minasato School,{p} I have found the seventh.{p} I have really seen it!」"
    ko "「水乡学校七大不可思议，{p}正好是七个哦。{p}真的有第七个！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1321
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_278596ab:

    # su "「Is that so?」"
    su "「是那样的么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1322
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_36076eca:

    # fn "「This is the first time I've heard that.」"
    fn "「我也是第一次听说呢。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1326
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_1480afea:

    # ko "「Yeah. From what I've investigated,{p} there shouldn't be any doubt.{p} Those documents weren't easy to find...」"
    ko "「嗯。从我调查的结果来看，{p}应该不会有错。{p}那些资料可不好找……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1330
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_ef4e4a06:

    # "Nyahaha.{p}Kounosuke gives a deceiving laugh."
    "喵哈哈。{p}孝之助露出了糊弄人的笑容。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1331
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_d0c52a67:

    # "Hmm.{p}I've never heard this gossip before,{p}that Kounosuke is revealing."
    "嗯——{p}那种传言我完全没听说过，{p}况且还是孝之助的情报！"

# game/day 6.rpy:1335
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_e7de53c3:

    # ko "「D-don't take my intelligence work...{p} so lightly!」"
    ko "「别、别小看我的情报网！"

# game/day 6.rpy:1336
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_e03ceab1:

    # fn "「N-no, I'm not...」"
    fn "「没、没有啊……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1337
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_507a1da5:

    # "Kounosuke is being strangely on edge."
    "孝之助在奇怪的方面格外敏锐呢。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1341
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_c588a90c:

    # ko "「Really?」"
    ko "「真没那么想？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1342
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_2ddbceb5:

    # fn "「Really. Anyways...{p} we've decided our teams.{p} Let's hurry up and go.」"
    fn "「真的啦。比起那个……{p}既然已经决定好分组了，{p}就快点开始吧。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1348
translate chinese_simplified day06_testbegin_7c95f73b:

    # "So we went,{p}and made our way into the building."
    "于是，我们走进了校舍里。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1371
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_efec7492:

    # "The library."
    "图书室。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1372
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b996ea77:

    # "There's a rumor that there's,{p}\"The Enthusiastic Bookworm\" here."
    "这里的传闻是，{p}「热心的读者」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1373
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_5c340ebd:

    # "Apparently,{p}there was a student who loved books."
    "好像是说，{p}有一个非常喜欢看书的学生。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1374
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_ca16c22e:

    # "But right before graduation,{p}they died in a freak accident..."
    "但是在毕业之前，{p}因意外事故死了……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1375
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b27c0838:

    # "However, that kid still loves books,{p}and has been haunting the library,{p}even beyond the grave."
    "但他因为太喜欢看书了，{p}即使死了之后，{p}还留在图书馆里继续读书。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1376
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e1db17a0:

    # "Recently, an unknown student has been seen,{p}reading in this library."
    "据说会看到一个不认识的学生，{p}在图书馆里看书。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1377
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3e397050:

    # "However, when you take your eyes off of him,{p}even just for a moment,{p}he disappears completely."
    "但是只要把眼睛稍微移开一下，{p}哪怕只是一瞬间，{p}那个人就完全消失了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1378
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_1bb3f66d:

    # "Either that,{p}or you can see a faint outline of a person."
    "或者，{p}只能看到模模糊糊的人影。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1379
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_f4083f3a:

    # "As far as I know,{p}the only sighting of one of the wonders,{p}has only been in this library."
    "而且据我所知，{p}七大不可思议中，{p}只有这里有目击证明。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1385
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_1174efcb:

    # ko "「Huh?」"
    ko "「哎呀？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1386
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e13737bf:

    # fn "「Looks like it's locked...」"
    fn "「好像锁上了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1392
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_90251856:

    # ko "「Crap. Oh well...」"
    ko "「切。真没办法……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1399
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_c11fcae7:

    # "Kounosuke looks disappointed,{p}but if it's locked,{p}there's nothing he can do."
    "孝之助看起来很失望，{p}但锁住了也没辙。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1400
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_5ca0c034:

    # "I feel discouraged right from the start,{p}but I take a picture for now.{p}We decide to go to our next location."
    "没想到一开始就碰一鼻子灰，{p}总之先拍照吧。{p}之后我们向下一个地方移动。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1404
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_1c8dfe7d:

    # fn "「Is everywhere...{p} going to be locked up like this?」"
    fn "「这样看来……{p} 别的地方会不会也锁上了？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1408
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_5e5b947f:

    # ko "「[fn], stop it,{p} don't say such negative things!」"
    ko "「博行，不要说，{p}不要说那么不吉利的话嘛！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1409
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_8841c518:

    # fn "「But isn't that normal for a school?」"
    fn "「但一般来说，学校不都是这样的么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1413
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_87bd264f:

    # ko "「I thought that, you know...{p} the security would be a little more lax.」"
    ko "「我想不会那么严的吧……{p} 」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1417
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_7b1d803c:

    # ko "「If push comes to shove,{p} I'll look for the key in the staff room.」"
    ko "「嘛，那样的话，{p} 去职员室找钥匙吧―――」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1418
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_09d029ad:

    # fn "「That wouldn't be a good idea...」"
    fn "「太离谱了吧！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1422
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_23875479:

    # ko "「Eh? I know that's bad!{p} It was simply a joke. Really...」"
    ko "「哎？我知道那样不好！{p} 只是开玩笑啦。真的……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1423
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_fd675c22:

    # "That was definitely not a joke..."
    "刚才那绝不是开玩笑……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1424
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_8d02fa4e:

    # "Really, in the end,{p}I was right about keeping watch over him."
    "真是的……{p}看来监视他真是太正确了！"

# game/day 6.rpy:1430
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_f50ebd3c:

    # "The gym."
    "体育馆。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1431
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_41a18230:

    # "It's rumored that,{p}\"The Headless Basketball Player\" is here."
    "这里的传闻是，{p}「没有头的篮球选手」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1432
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_4f1d81bd:

    # "One night,{p}there were noises coming from the gym."
    "深夜，{p}有声音从体育馆里传来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1433
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3df5086c:

    # "The teacher on night duty looked in,{p}and saw one of the students,{p}practicing basketball."
    "值班的老师往里一看，{p}看到一个学生{p}在那里练习篮球。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1434
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_ab6cbc5c:

    # "Thinking it was a strange time for that,{p}the teacher carefully went into the gym."
    "老师还在想这个时间练习真是奇怪呢，{p}于是进入体育馆想要提醒那个学生。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1435
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_51ea911d:

    # "But upon a closer look,{p}the kid had no head."
    "但是走近一看，{p}那个孩子没有脑袋。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1436
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_21c9fd09:

    # "And where the kid's head should've been,{p}there was a ball instead."
    "而在他脑袋的位置，{p}取而代之的是一个篮球。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1437
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_055bd458:

    # "The teacher found the boy's head.{p}With a broad grin,{p}it looked at the teacher and laughed."
    "老师找到了少年的头。{p}那个头一脸坏笑，{p}看着老师笑了起来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1438
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_98650e06:

    # "Then, it disappeared along with the body."
    "然后就连同身体一起消失了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1447
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_9e495846:

    # ko "「By the way [fn],{p} do you know if that rumor is true?」"
    ko "「说起来博行，{p} 你知道这里真正的传闻么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1448
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_da314ab0:

    # fn "「You mean...{p} about the headless basketball player?」"
    fn "「你是说……{p} 没有头的篮球选手？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1449
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_82385af0:

    # ko "「Not that,{p} the part at the end of the story.」"
    ko "「不是那个啦，{p} 是那个故事的结局。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1450
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bd6a7173:

    # fn "「The teacher found a ghost,{p} then it laughed and disappeared.」"
    fn "「幽灵看到老师后，{p} 笑着消失了。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1454
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e4f80b6f:

    # ko "「That's not right.」"
    ko "「不对。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1455
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b5ad05af:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    fn "「哎？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1459
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_c2cb47ad:

    # ko "「That's actually an old rumor.」"
    ko "「其实那是以前的传闻。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1460
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_746f929c:

    # ko "「When the teacher found the ghost,{p} it walked up to the teacher,{p} and said \"I'm sorry.\""
    ko "「老师发现幽灵后，{p} 幽灵走到老师面前，{p} 说了句『对不起』。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1461
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_adbcddc4:

    # ko "Then, it thanked him,{p} and disappeared.」"
    ko "然后，道了谢，{p} 就消失了。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1462
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_7d79085b:

    # ko "「There's no laughing part of the story,{p} and besides, back then,{p} volleyball was the popular sport."
    ko "「故事里根本没有笑的场景，{p} 而且，那时候，{p} 流行的运动其实是排球。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1463
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_f8f02668:

    # ko "The story has changed a lot.」"
    ko "所以故事被改了很多。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1464
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_049313c2:

    # fn "「Ehh...」"
    fn "「嘿……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1465
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_8ab1f953:

    # ko "「Perhaps the polite ghost wasn't scary enough?{p} So somebody changed it,{p} to make it more interesting."
    ko "「大概是觉得有礼貌的幽灵不够恐怖吧？{p} 所以有人就把它改了，{p} 让它变得更有趣。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1466
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_9a9ed6cb:

    # ko "They probably also changed the sport,{p} so it would seem more current.」"
    ko "可能还把运动也改成了流行的运动。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1467
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_41b1f9ac:

    # "That's very detailed, Kounosuke."
    "真了解呢，孝之助。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1471
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bc4db824:

    # ko "「This perfectly matches my data!」"
    ko "「关于这七大不可思议，我可是好好调查过了呢！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1472
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_832d6dbc:

    # "I'm impressed.{p}Kounosuke gives the V sign."
    "我正佩服他呢，{p}孝之助摆出了胜利的姿势。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1473
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b0dd6699:

    # ko "「Didn't I tell you?{p} Don't underestimate my intelligence network!」"
    ko "「说过了吧？{p} 不要小看我的情报网呢！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1474
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bd2e0b56:

    # "Ah, I'm still concerned..."
    "真是的，还在意着呢……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1480
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_af7e584e:

    # "The art room."
    "图工室。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1481
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_be96a507:

    # "To be honest,{p}I don't understand these rumors."
    "这里的传闻，{p}不太好说清。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1482
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_039783d1:

    # "At night you can see a disembodied soul,{p}a shadow drawing,{p}a picture of Mona Lisa that moves,"
    "深夜能看到游荡的鬼魂，{p}画画的人影，{p}会动的蒙娜丽莎画像，"

# game/day 6.rpy:1483
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_d6755fe4:

    # "a sculpture of Mona Lisa that talks,{p}or even a ghost that makes sculptures..."
    "会说话的蒙娜丽莎石膏像，{p}甚至是制作雕塑的幽灵……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1484
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_181bad6b:

    # "The list goes on and on.{p}If I recall correctly, they call this place,{p}\"The Arts and Crafts Room of Mystery.\""
    "各种各样的传闻层出不穷。{p}如果没记错的话，{p}这里叫做「图工室的怪事」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1485
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_cf6a3033:

    # fn "「So, anyways...」"
    fn "「话虽如此……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1486
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e9cd621c:

    # "Why is it that...{p}there are so many rumors about this place?"
    "为什么……{p}一说图工室就有那么多令人不舒服的东西呢。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1487
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_fb49202a:

    # "The Mona Lisa is hanging on the wall,{p}and there are sculped faces,{p}and hands at the back of the room."
    "墙壁上挂着的蒙娜丽莎画像，{p}教室后面摆放的头和手的石膏像，"

# game/day 6.rpy:1488
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_0881b3b7:

    # "It feels creepy enough by itself,{p}and shining a light through the darkness,{p}makes it extra eerie."
    "只是这些就够让人不舒服的了，{p}再加上昏暗的手电光一照，{p}更多了几分恐怖。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1495
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e7f890e9:

    # "...but this eerie atmosphere...{p}it doesn't seem to affect Kounosuke at all..."
    "……但是这种诡异的氛围……{p}似乎对孝之助一点影响也没有……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1499
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_450c0e81:

    # ko "「Well then [fn],{p} we should be getting back soon.」"
    ko "「那博行，{p} 差不多该回去了吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1500
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_cb997b98:

    # fn "「Y-you know, Kounosuke,{p} aren't you being pretty slow?」"
    fn "「那……那个，孝之助，{p} 你也太迟钝了吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1504
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_dd9a6cdd:

    # ko "「What's with you all of a sudden?{p} That's rude...」"
    ko "「你怎么突然这么说？{p} 真没礼貌……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1505
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_631fc418:

    # fn "「No, it's just...」"
    fn "「不，只是……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1506
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3df7d2aa:

    # "No, I don't believe.{p}But even though I don't believe,{p}this place still..."
    "不，并不是我相信这些。{p}但即使不相信，{p}这种地方还是让人不舒服……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1507
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_0a510387:

    # "...just doesn't have a good feeling."
    "……就是感觉不太好。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1511
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_159ccb01:

    # ko "「This is the place, right?{p} Where all the ghost stories are about?」"
    ko "「就是这里吧？{p} 那些鬼故事说的就是这里？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1512
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_cd14ea49:

    # fn "「Y-yeah. It is,{p} but what do you have to say about it?」"
    fn "「额……嗯。是的，{p} 但你怎么看呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1513
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_ff89e701:

    # "Why is he so... calm?"
    "为什么他会那么……淡定？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1514
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_155ac0ca:

    # "While Kounosuke searches for something,{p}I roll my eyes in complaint."
    "孝之助好像在寻找什么东西似的，{p}而我只是翻着白眼。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1515
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_2222935b:

    # "Then, he points his light at a single picture."
    "之后，他把灯光照向了一幅画。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1520
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_711a5ee6:

    # ko "「That's the picture.」"
    ko "「就是这幅画。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1521
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b5fb207e:

    # fn "「What?」"
    fn "「什么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1522
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_39955e9c:

    # ko "「One of the wonders...{p} of the arts and crafts room.」"
    ko "「七大不可思议之一……{p} 图工室的。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1523
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_35971d16:

    # "The picture was drawn with crayons.{p}It was probably drawn unskillfully,{p}by some elementary school kid."
    "那幅画是用蜡笔画的。{p}大概是什么小学生{p}画的很拙劣的画吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1524
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_64977515:

    # "There's the school building,{p}and a lot of kids are playing."
    "画着学校的教学楼，{p}很多孩子在玩耍。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1525
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_c747bc16:

    # "Someone is wearing a red and white hat,{p}this is a picture of sports day."
    "有人戴着红白帽子，{p}这是运动会的画吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1526
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3ad16c57:

    # "This picture isn't all that realistic,{p}and I don't feel anything weird about it."
    "这画没有什么特别的真实感，{p}也没有什么奇怪的感觉。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1527
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_761ab2eb:

    # "Instead, I'm definitely more afraid...{p}of that Mona Lisa on the wall."
    "相对的，我更害怕的……{p}是墙上那幅蒙娜丽莎画像。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1528
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_369fb1c6:

    # "I wonder...{p}What does this have to do the the rumors?"
    "我在想……{p}这和鬼故事有什么关系呢？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1529
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_a6ee0236:

    # ko "「Apparently, a ghost drew this picture.」"
    ko "「这个呢，是幽灵画的哦。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1530
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_1a9070f2:

    # fn "「A ghost drew it...?」"
    fn "「幽灵画的……？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1531
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bcda7578:

    # ko "「The rumor here is called \"The Lonely Artist\".{p} A long time ago at this school,{p} there was a student with a very frail body.」"
    ko "「这里的传闻叫做「寂寞的画家」。{p} 很久以前，这所学校里，{p} 有一个体质很差的学生。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1532
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_1a2dec02:

    # "He wanted to play with the other students,{p}but he couldn't.{p}He had lunch instead of gym class."
    "想和其他同学一起玩，{p}却不能玩。{p}午休和体育课的时候只能待在图工室。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1533
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_c7f84635:

    # "So, from this room,{p}he watched the schoolyard instead,{p}and drew pictures."
    "所以，他就从这个房间，{p}看着校园，{p}画画。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1534
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_2f5d0c08:

    # "While the others were in the schoolyard playing,{p}he would secretly mix himself in with them."
    "其他人在校园里玩的时候，{p}他就把自己偷偷画到大伙之中。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1535
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_649b8588:

    # "However, that student's disease got worse,{p}and he died."
    "但是，那个学生的病情恶化了，{p}最后死去了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1536
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3724af6c:

    # "After that,{p}the student settled down into his drawing."
    "之后，{p}那个学生就住进了自己画的画里。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1537
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_4c2d43ea:

    # "He said that now,{p}he could play with everybody in it."
    "他说现在，{p}可以和画里的大家一起玩了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1538
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_379595d5:

    # "This is where the story gets weird..."
    "故事从这里开始变得奇怪了……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1539
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_c5f6ad1b:

    # "When you look into that picture,{p}it sucks you in.{p}No, it turns you into a sculpture!"
    "看着那幅画，{p}就会被吸进画里。{p}不对，是变成石膏像！"

# game/day 6.rpy:1540
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b7527f4b:

    # "The Mona Lisa and the boys are friends,{p}and every night they talk to each other."
    "蒙娜丽莎和孩子们是朋友，{p}每天晚上都会互相聊天。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1541
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_7310ed64:

    # "No no, the Mona Lisa talks to the sculptures.{p}The Mona Lisa turns students into sculptures."
    "不对不对，是蒙娜丽莎在和石膏像说话。{p}把学生变成石膏的是蒙娜丽莎。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1542
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_eeddeb62:

    # "Don't know what happened with the original story.{p}But they go on and on like that."
    "搞不清原始的故事到底是怎么回事了。{p}但传闻就这样越来越离谱了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1543
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_25f398e7:

    # "That's why it really is,{p}\"The Arts and Crafts Room of Mystery.\""
    "所以这里确实是，{p}「图工室的怪事」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1549
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_1205dd1a:

    # ko "「Besides, ghosts were originally people,{p} right [fn]?"
    ko "「而且，幽灵原本也是人类吧，{p} 博行？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1550
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_6ddcbe3e:

    # ko "So when you think about it,{p} there's nothing to be afraid of."
    ko "那样想的话，{p} 就没什么可怕的了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1551
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3433eaba:

    # ko "Curiously enough,{p} you know what I'm more afraid of?{p} Having an annoying partner!」"
    ko "说起来好笑，{p} 你知道我更怕什么吗？{p} 就是有一个烦人的搭档！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1552
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_204b18a6:

    # fn "「I-I see...」"
    fn "「原……原来如此……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1553
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3ea72f3e:

    # "I think his reasoning is mixed up,{p}but Kounosuke appears to be composed about it."
    "虽然总觉得他的理由很牵强，{p}但孝之助看来确实很淡定。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1558
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_9f5b7a72:

    # ko "「Incidentally,{p} the student who painted this picture,{p} is actually still perfectly alive.」"
    ko "「顺带一提，{p} 画这幅画的学生，{p} 其实还活得好好的呢。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1559
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b5ad05af_1:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    fn "「哎？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1560
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_6b7dd9f3:

    # ko "「Have you not noticed it yet, [fn]?」"
    ko "「博行，你还没注意到么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1561
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_f583e471:

    # "To see why Kounosuke is laughing,{p}I take another close look at the picture."
    "为了看清楚孝之助为什么在笑，{p}我又仔细看了一遍那幅画。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1566
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_f2581fae:

    # "Come to think of it,{p}before I transferred,{p}I think I saw this picture."
    "说起来，{p}转校之前，{p}我好像见过这幅画。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1567
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_9fe499bf:

    # "It says:{p}[fn] [ln], 5th Year"
    "上面写着：{p}西村　博行，五年级"

# game/day 6.rpy:1568
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_9f207758:

    # "This is my drawing!"
    "这不是我画的么！"

# game/day 6.rpy:1574
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_6a4066e6:

    # ko "「Did I fool you?」"
    ko "「上当了吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1575
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_28037562:

    # fn "「I completely fell for it...」"
    fn "「真是完全被你耍了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1579
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_5db10ed7:

    # ko "「Sorry, sorry.{p} But what I said earlier is true."
    ko "「抱歉抱歉。{p} 不过之前说的都是真的哦。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1580
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_29995fb7:

    # ko "Unfortunately though,{p} the ghost's drawing has never been found.」"
    ko "只是很遗憾，{p} 幽灵画的画还没有找到。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1581
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_272f556b:

    # fn "「Is that right...」"
    fn "「啊啊是吗……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1582
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_654b0162:

    # "Afterwards,{p}he had so much fun fooling me,{p}that for the whole time,"
    "之后，{p}他耍我耍得那么高兴，{p}以至于一整段时间，"

# game/day 6.rpy:1583
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b5ec89bd:

    # "a smile stuck to his face."
    "他的脸上一直挂着笑容。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1584
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bf6b53a4:

    # "...I'll get even some day."
    "……总有一天我会奉还给他的！"

# game/day 6.rpy:1591
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_5f78cc22:

    # "We went back to the entranceway,{p}and it appears that we are early,{p}as the other two still had not gotten back."
    "回到门口一看，{p}看来我们比较快呢，{p}另外两人还没回来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1592
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b3a52af6:

    # "We just have to wait,{p}but Kounosuke can't sit still.{p}He keeps clicking his shutter at things."
    "只能等着了，{p}但孝之助闲不住。{p}他还对着鞋柜拍个不停。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1596
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_add0cecb:

    # ko "「They're both slow.」"
    ko "「那两人可真慢啊！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1597
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_a52bd548:

    # fn "「Kounosuke's the one saying that...?」"
    fn "「孝之助居然说别人慢……？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1598
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bee236c8:

    # "However, they sure are taking their time.{p}Maybe I should go look for them?{p}But I might miss them."
    "话虽如此……他们确实用了不少时间。{p}我是不是该去找找呢？{p}但如果错过了怎么办。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1607
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_22448e14:

    # "Ah, are they coming?"
    "啊，他们回来了么？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1608
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_270fd6d3:

    # torashun "「G-g-g-g...」"
    torashun "「出……出出出……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1613
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_92d478da:

    # torashun "{size=+30}「GET OUT!!」"
    torashun "{size=+30}「出现啦！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1617
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_fe8fd4fb:

    # fn "「Geh, T-Torahi... you're back...」"
    fn "「唔咕，虎……虎彦……你回来了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1623
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3b871877:

    # to "「We gotta get out of here!{p} We saw it!」"
    to "「出现了！{p} 我看到了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1627
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_26597a9e:

    # su "「[fn]-san, please help!」"
    su "「博行救命啊！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1628
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_9f005214:

    # fn "「P-please, y-you're gonna kill me!」"
    fn "「求……求你，你……你要勒死我了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1637
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e470e712:

    # ko "「Torahiko, what are you doing!?{p} [fn]'s going to die!」"
    ko "「虎彦，你在干什么！{p} 博行要挂了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1641
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bc9b771a:

    # to "「It's not that!{p} Look, right over there」"
    to "「不是说那个！{p} 你看，就在那边！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1642
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_9751c64c:

    # fn "「Guh...」"
    fn "「唔咕……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1643
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_0b0de622:

    # "Right over there,{p}in front of me,{p}I can see the River Styx..."
    "就在那边，{p}在我面前，{p}我已经能看到三途河了……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1644
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b20686a9:

    # "Once I recover from a lack of oxygen,{p}I understand what's going on, but...{p}Aah, my vision is blurry..."
    "缺氧恢复之后，{p}总算理解了状况，但是……{p}啊啊，眼睛好朦胧……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1645
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_7a216d71:

    # "I feel like I'm seriously going to fall down.{p}While trying to keep my consciousness,{p}I look up and see that those two have arrived."
    "感觉真的要晕倒了。{p}尽力保持意识，{p}我抬头看到那两人已经到了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1653
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_b1344ca8:

    # "That's... what?"
    "那是……什么？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1664
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e2216ba0:

    # ko "「Eh?」"
    ko "「哎？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1665
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_58ceee43:

    # to "「Ah...」"
    to "「啊……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1666
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_21620e98:

    # su "「Huh?」"
    su "「哎？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1667
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_6260c19c:

    # "I hear their three dumbfounded voices."
    "我听到了他们三人惊讶的声音。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1668
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_a692c971:

    # "Choking, I try to bring air into my lungs,{p}I look in the same direction, and..."
    "使劲地大吸了一口气，{p}我向同样的方向看去……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1674
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_bc149c47:

    # fn "「Eh, Botan, teacher?」"
    fn "「哎？牡丹……老师？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1680
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_4620e060:

    # bo "{size=+15}「WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE,{p} AT A TIME LIKE THIS!!??」"
    bo "{size=+15}「你们在这里做什么，{p} 这种时间来学校！！？？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1711
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_f873d445:

    # to "「I told you!{p} This was a bad idea from the beginning!」"
    to "「我就说了吧！{p} 一开始就不该来的！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1715
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_af165e6a:

    # su "「Ooh, my head hurts...」"
    su "「呜呜……头好疼……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1719
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_4fe839f1:

    # to "「Kounosuke, this is all your fault.」"
    to "「孝之助，都怪你！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1723
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e2963a09:

    # ko "「S-sorry...」"
    ko "「对……对不起嘛……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1724
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_3f762980:

    # fn "「But Torahiko, that was really tight.{p} I thought I nearly saw the River Styx...」"
    fn "「但是虎彦，你勒得太紧了。{p} 我都快看到三途河了……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1725
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_15378d4d:

    # "I had seen the Styx,{p}but just for an instant,{p}I saw something strange."
    "我看到了三途河，{p}不过只是一瞬间，{p}我也看到了奇怪的东西。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1726
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_0c563afa:

    # to "「Eh? Oh, r-really?」"
    to "「哎？啊，是……是吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1730
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_51a0b84e:

    # ko "「All brawn and no brains!」"
    ko "「体力白痴～！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1734
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e08cbaed:

    # to "「What!?{p} But it was you in the first place-」"
    to "「什么！{p} 还不都是因为你――」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1735
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_0660b0fe:

    # fn "「Come on now...」"
    fn "「好啦好啦……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1736
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_e6cb142c:

    # "I try to calm those two down,{p}and call out to Shun-kun,{p}who was completely in the outfield."
    "我试着让那两人冷静下来，{p}并叫上峻君，{p}他完全被晾在了一边。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1737
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_c8b7ed06:

    # "Since the test of courage,{p}we were noisy all the way home."
    "试胆回去的路上，{p}我们一直吵吵闹闹的。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1747
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_49ffd2b8:

    # "On the way back,\nTorahiko was still complaining,{p}but even after all that,"
    "回去的路上，\n虎彦一直在抱怨，{p}即使这样，"

# game/day 6.rpy:1748
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_42001b18:

    # "I don't know if Kounosuke even understood."
    "我也不知道孝之助到底有没有听懂。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1749
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_040eed85:

    # "While those two are arguing,{p}I try to calm Shun-kun."
    "那两人在吵架的时候，{p}我试着安抚峻君。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1750
translate chinese_simplified day06_kounotest_37dced13:

    # "Which reminded me, before I transferred,{p}the mood was always like this.{p}I've missed this."
    "说起来，转校之前，{p}气氛一直就是这样的。{p}好怀念啊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1762
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_f50ebd3c:

    # "The gym."
    "体育馆。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1763
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_669b75fe:

    # "There's a rumor of a \"headless basketball player\" here."
    "这里的传闻是「没有头的篮球选手」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1764
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_2942d6fe:

    # "One night, there were noises coming from the gym.{p}The teacher on night duty looked in,{p}and saw one of the students practicing basketball."
    "深夜，从体育馆里有声音传来，{p}值班的老师往里面一窥，{p}看到一个学生在练习篮球。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1765
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_494ff6f8:

    # "Thinking it was a strange time to be doing that,{p}the teacher carefully went into the gym."
    "还想呢，这个时间还在练习真奇怪呢，{p}老师想要提醒一下学生，于是进入体育馆。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1766
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_51ea911d:

    # "But upon a closer look,{p}the kid had no head."
    "但是，走近一看{p}那个孩子没有脑袋。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1767
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_53b83920:

    # "And where his head should've been,{p}there was a ball."
    "再一看，{p}手里的篮球就是他的头。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1768
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_055bd458:

    # "The teacher found the boy's head.{p}With a broad grin,{p}it looked at the teacher and laughed."
    "少年的头看到老师之后，{p}冲着老师撇嘴一笑，"

# game/day 6.rpy:1769
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_98650e06:

    # "Then, it disappeared along with the body."
    "然后连同身体立即消失了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1773
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_7576c596:

    # to "「Th-there's nothing here.」"
    to "「什，什么都没有嘛！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1777
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_2c259edc:

    # fn "「Torahiko, you're grabbing my arm too tight.」"
    fn "「虎彦，你握的太紧了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1781
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c0980ec8:

    # to "「Ah, s-sorry...」"
    to "「啊，抱，抱歉」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1785
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_11bedf1c:

    # "Hmm..."
    "嗯……"

# game/day 6.rpy:1786
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_36af1adc:

    # "He lets go for a moment,{p}but a few steps later he grabs back on again."
    "虽然虎彦放开了，{p}但是刚走没两步，就又抓住我的胳膊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1787
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_5ddfb812:

    # "It's not that I don't like this,{p}I just wish his grip was a little weaker."
    "虽然不讨厌，{p}不过要是力量小点就好了..."

# game/day 6.rpy:1794
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c2ac0d26:

    # fn "「You know Torahiko,{p} I was just thinking something earlier.」"
    fn "「那个，虎彦，{p}刚才我就这么想了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1798
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_8a1afc79:

    # to "「Wh-what?」"
    to "「怎、{w=.3}怎么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1799
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_1a1fa448:

    # fn "「Torahiko, are you scared?」"
    fn "「虎彦害怕么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1803
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_a9da0093:

    # to "「I-I'm not scared!」"
    to "「才...{w=.3}才不害怕呢！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1807
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_d0b6b3b6:

    # to "「I'm not afraid, not at all.{p} But I don't like this.」"
    to "「虽然完全不害怕...{p}但不擅长应付这类事...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1808
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_6276e3fa:

    # fn "「Doesn't that just mean you're scared...?」"
    fn "「那不还是害怕么……？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1812
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_7a84ca55:

    # to "「I'm not scared, that's not it!」"
    to "「说了不害怕了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1813
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_e95b58ce:

    # fn "「Uh huh, sure...」"
    fn "「是是，{w=.3}嗯」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1814
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_898f5d6e:

    # "Well, I'll just leave it at that for now."
    "嘛...总之就当是那样吧。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1815
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c5cd81ab:

    # "Perhaps I've been in a bad mood since we came in.{p}I wasn't amazed with Kounosuke's plan."
    "莫非从入口开始就害怕了，{p}并不是觉得孝之助的主意讨厌"

# game/day 6.rpy:1816
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0b78d23c:

    # "I didn't want to do a test of courage,{p}so why are we doing this?"
    "我不想做胆量测试，{p}那为什么还要做呢？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1823
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_8aab5fb5:

    # "The stairs on the north side of the school building."
    "校舍背面的楼梯。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1824
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_467c90d8:

    # "The wonder here is called,{p}\"The Spiral Staircase of Evil\"."
    "这里的七大不可思议之一是「魔力的螺旋楼梯」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1825
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_a89bb87e:

    # "The stairs are connected to a mysterious space,{p}and if you're just walking absentmindedly,{p}you'll never make it to the next floor."
    "这个楼梯连接着另一个空间{p}如果一边想事一边发呆地走，{p}无论如何也走不到下一层。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1826
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_24577939:

    # "At the landing of the stairs,{p}there are mirrors that can lead to the underworld.{p}And if you leap into them, you can go there."
    "在楼梯的平台处，{p}有通向冥界的镜子。{p}跳进去的话就能去到那里。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1827
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_3559f2e5:

    # "There are a bunch of other stories like that."
    "别的地方也有类似的故事。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1831
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ee17320d:

    # to "「......」"
    to "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1836
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_cb2f32cf:

    # fn "「......」"
    fn "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1837
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ee17320d_1:

    # to "「......」"
    to "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1844
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_cb2f32cf_1:

    # fn "「......」"
    fn "「……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1845
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0979c0b4:

    # "For some time now,{p}Torahiko has been holding onto my arm."
    "从刚才开始，虎彦就一直抓着我的胳膊。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1846
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_e435583b:

    # "I'm afraid to be afraid...{p}But the one next to me is so scared,{p}that it calms me down for some reason."
    "虽然我不是很害怕……{p}但是旁边的虎彦一直发抖，{p}不知怎的弄得我也有点发冷。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1847
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c612c546:

    # "My arm is simply in pain.{p}Torahiko is hopless like this.{p}I wasn't expecting him to be like that."
    "胳膊真是好疼啊。{p}看来这家伙只是身体变大了而已{p}没想到他会变成这样。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1854
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_19ee9f10:

    # "I face towards the mirror and click my shutter,{p}finishing my quota for this area."
    "对着镜子照了照片，{p}这里的工作基本结束了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1855
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_5b3a97f7:

    # "Then, I immediately think about our next location.{p}But... there seems to be something...{p}something in the mirror."
    "正准备到下个地方去的时候{p}但是...似乎有什么...{p}在镜子里有什么东西。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1856
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0d3430b2:

    # "I stand still and call out to Torahiko."
    "我站住叫虎彦。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1860
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_1540e6e3:

    # fn "「T-Torahiko...?」"
    fn "「虎...虎彦...？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1861
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_8a1afc79_1:

    # to "「Wh-what?」"
    to "「怎...怎么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1862
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0f6569ea:

    # fn "「Th-the mirror...」"
    fn "「看...看镜子……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1863
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_803abfaa:

    # to "「The mirror?」"
    to "「镜子？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1864
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_9fa55e25:

    # fn "「On your shoulder!」"
    fn "「虎彦的肩膀...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1865
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_b17e66c1:

    # "We both look into the mirror,{p}a hand reaches out from behind Torahiko..."
    "两个人看着镜子里，{p}从虎彦的背后伸出一只手来..."

# game/day 6.rpy:1869
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_832fb31b:

    # to "{size=+15}{nw}"
    to "{size=+15}{nw}"

# game/day 6.rpy:1871
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_47a1ad36:

    # extend "「UWAAAAAA!!」"
    extend "「呜哇啊啊啊啊！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1875
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_7b599dcd:

    # "The moment he sees that,{p}Torahiko runs to dash up the stairs."
    "看到那一幕的瞬间，{p}虎彦用冲刺的速度逃上了楼梯。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1876
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_6a93bd66:

    # "I chase after him in hot haste,{p}and catch him as he's climbing the staircase."
    "我也慌慌张张地追了上去，{p}终于在最上层把虎彦抓到了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1880
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ff958beb:

    # "We safely make it to the next floor.{p}There aren't any more stairs that lead up."
    "没问题，我们已经爬得很高了。{p}证据就是已经没有往上的楼梯了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1884
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c97f0c5b:

    # to "「Th-th-that thing appeared.{p} It did, didn't it?{p} Did you see it? J-just now?」"
    to "「出...{w=.3}出现了。{p}出现了吧？{p}刚...？{p}刚才看到没有{w=.3}」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1885
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_5ebc66e7:

    # "He is completely shocked.{p}I purposely grin and laugh at Torahiko."
    "看到狼狈不堪的虎彦，{p}我故意笑了起来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1886
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_dc50e1e5:

    # fn "「Yep. That hand that appeared behind you,{p} was my hand!」"
    fn "「嗯。{p}从虎彦背后伸出了手，{p}做出了胜利的姿势。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1887
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_e9f199fe:

    # "Then, I give him the V sign."
    "说着，我摆出了胜利的姿势。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1891
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_1d58e3e9:

    # fn "{size=+15}「The Paranormal Phenomena.」"
    fn "{size=+15}「啊?{w=.3}灵异现象」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1895
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_3d0c59dd:

    # to "「[fn]!!」"
    to "「博行～！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1900
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0e661131:

    # fn "「Uncle, uncle!{p} You're squeezing me too much!」"
    fn "「只是惨叫声……啊，{p}抱得太紧了，太紧了」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1901
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_dec28f60:

    # to "「Shut up!」"
    to "「啰嗦！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1902
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_a0cab23c:

    # "I-I didn't think it would work this well."
    "没，没想到会变成这样。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1903
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_45551b74:

    # "While receiving a jokingly strong headlock,{p}I desperately apologize to him."
    "他用比玩笑时候还大的力气夹着我的头，{p}我很认真地向他道歉。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1910
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_350a535e:

    # fn "「But still,{p} you're such a scaredy cat, Torahiko.」"
    fn "「话虽如此，{p}虎彦真的很害怕哪~~」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1914
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_4ef00125:

    # to "「There's nothing I'm afraid of!{p} It's just that...{p} I-I don't like this kind of stuff!」"
    to "「才没有害怕！{p}只是有点...{p}我不擅长应付这类事！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1915
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_b2d8654a:

    # fn "「Hahaha!」"
    fn "「哈哈哈！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1916
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_acb1b6f1:

    # "I wish he would just admit it already."
    "明明承认就好了嘛。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1917
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_fcc035a5:

    # "For him to be so panicked,{p}and yet still desperately deny it,{p}is so adorable, and makes me laugh."
    "狼狈成那样的虎彦{p}还在拼命地掩饰，真是好可爱{p}弄得我都笑出来了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1921
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_f1706068:

    # to "「It's true!{p} Really, I'm not s-scared at all!」"
    to "「是真的！{p}我真的一点都不害怕--！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1928
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_99c2e16c:

    # "At the other end of the darkness,{p}I hear a sound."
    "从黑暗深处传过来的声音。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1929
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_63a85cc1:

    # "Not only does Torahiko freeze,{p}but I do too."
    "不光是虎彦，连我都懵在那里了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1930
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0dd57784:

    # "In the completely silent school building,{p}there is certainly a ticking sound."
    "万籁俱寂的学校里，的确是有声音。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1934
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_b9978ac7:

    # "It's the sound of a metronome,{p}swaying back and forth..."
    "那是节拍器左右摇摆的声音..."

# game/day 6.rpy:1935
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_85302826:

    # "It's ahead of us.{p}The music room.{p}The wonder there is \"The Shapeless Musician\"."
    "在前面的是，{p}音乐室。{p}那里的七大不可思议之一是「无形的音乐家」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1936
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c87a814b:

    # "When the room should be empty,{p}you can hear the sound of a piano."
    "空无一人的音乐教室里传来了钢琴的声音，"

# game/day 6.rpy:1937
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_2de6f31d:

    # "The metronome, which hasn't been touched,{p}is said to start ticking its own rhythm."
    "没有人碰过的节拍器，{p}据说会自动地打起拍子。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1941
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ba699563:

    # to "「A-are we going in there?」"
    to "「要...{w=.3}要去嘛？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1942
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c76f6bf5:

    # fn "「Wh-what should we do?」"
    fn "「怎...{w=.3}怎么办...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1946
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_3c414d64:

    # to "「It's too dangerous!」"
    to "「肯定会糟糕的！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1947
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_24808def:

    # fn "「B-but then we won't get any pictures.」"
    fn "「但{w=.3}不拍照的话...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1948
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_6433cd54:

    # "It's not just about Kounosuke,{p}It's about Shun-kun too."
    "先不说孝之助，{p}峻君也来了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1949
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_449559df:

    # "As his senpai, if I were to say,{p}\"I couldn't take any pictures,{p}because I was too scared\","
    "作为前辈，如果我说{p}"因为害怕没能拍照"{p}的话"

# game/day 6.rpy:1950
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_9016ec86:

    # "that would be really lame."
    "就太没面子了！"

# game/day 6.rpy:1955
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_41dc9c95:

    # "Slowly approaching the music room,{p}the sound becomes clearer."
    "我们战战兢兢地靠近音乐室，{p}声音也变得清楚了。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1956
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_8a340617:

    # "There's no mistaking it,{p}that's the sound of a metronome."
    "没有听错，{p}是节拍器的声音。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1957
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_d142aa09:

    # "It's the middle of the night,{p}nobody could have mistakenly turned it on."
    "这样的深夜，{p}没有人会不小心打开它。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1958
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_865065ba:

    # "Also, it's Summer vacation,{p}so there's no reason for anybody to go in there."
    "而且是暑假，{p}没有理由会有人进去。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1959
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_00977869:

    # "I grab onto my camera with my sweaty palms.{p}Torahiko is hiding behind me,{p}and won't let go of my shirt."
    "握着相机的手在不断冒汗。{p}虎彦躲在我身后，{p}抓着衬衫不放。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1960
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_b3dee754:

    # "Huddled next to each other,{p}we stand before the music room's door,{p}which was ajar for some reason."
    "两个人紧挨着来到{p}音乐室半开的门前，{p}不知为什么门是开着的。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1961
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_4da61845:

    # "Gulp..."
    "吞口水的声音......"

# game/day 6.rpy:1962
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_db9cda7f:

    # "I make up my mind,{p}and boldly peer into the opening,{p}for just a moment."
    "在下定决心的那一瞬间{p}大胆地往门缝里窥探，{p}就看了一眼。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1974
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_18794df7:

    # fntora "{size=+40}「UWAAA!!」"
    fntora "{size=+40}「呜哇哇哇啊啊啊啊——」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1978
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_4e8896f9:

    # ko "「Great success!」"
    ko "「成功了吗~?」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1979
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_670bb9b5:

    # "A sudden flash of light comes from the music room.{p}Then, a familiar voice and,{p}illuminated by a flashlight, a familiar face."
    "音乐教室突然射出一道闪光。{p}然后听到了熟悉的声音，{p}还有被手电筒照着的熟悉的面孔。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1983
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_1ff89df1:

    # ko "「How was it? Were you surprised?」"
    ko "「怎么样？{p}吓到了吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1984
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c3165373:

    # "Why is Kounosuke here?{p}Great success?{p}Why is he laughing..."
    "为什么孝之助会在这？{p}成功了？？{p}为什么在笑..."

# game/day 6.rpy:1985
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_d17ad7c0:

    # "Err...{p}In other words, the metronome earlier..."
    "嗯....{p}也就是说刚才的节拍器是..."

# game/day 6.rpy:1986
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_e1745204:

    # "So it's like that?"
    "原来是那么回事吗？"

# game/day 6.rpy:1987
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_cbd1184b:

    # fntora "「Ko...」"
    fntora "「可.....」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1988
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_3d8e854d:

    # "Once I understand the source,{p}my fear from earlier disappears."
    "一知道原因，刚才的恐怖就全都消失了"

# game/day 6.rpy:1989
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c683191d:

    # "Something different fills my head instead,{p}and boils over."
    "取而代之的是充满大脑里沸腾的怒火{p}沸腾溢出。"

# game/day 6.rpy:1990
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_5a4d898b:

    # fntora "{size=+ 40}「KOUNOSUKE!!」"
    fntora "{size=+ 40}「孝之助！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1994
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_17a58cb3:

    # ko "「Th-that hurts, let me go!」"
    ko "「好{w=.3}好疼，好难受...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1995
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_1fa6baa4:

    # fntora "{size=+10}「SHUT UP!!」"
    fntora "{size=+10}「少啰嗦！！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:1996
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_2c7bca18:

    # "Torahiko puts him in a headlock,{p}and I use my rubbing combination technique."
    "虎彦对他来了个夹头，{p}而我使出了摩擦组合技。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2000
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_7518a1d8:

    # ko "「I-I'm dying!」"
    ko "「要{w=.3}要死啦！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2001
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_32237f6a:

    # "After a bit, we finally free him,{p}he holds his head and groans."
    "孝之助被一顿暴虐之后才被放开，{p}他抱着头悲鸣着。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2008
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_fabc47d2:

    # ko "「Oohh...」"
    ko "「呜呜呜......」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2009
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_14df2427:

    # fn "「That was a bad, good-for-nothing trick!」"
    fn "「无聊的恶作剧最差劲了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2010
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_a628e0f3:

    # to "「It's just as [fn] says!」"
    to "「博行说的没错！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2011
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_9c194789:

    # ko "「Oh, if I was a ghost,{p} I'd definitely haunt you...」"
    ko "「呜..我要是变成幽灵绝对会缠上你们的！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2012
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_9cbaa3cd:

    # "While cursing us out,{p}Kounosuke staggers over to the metronome,{p}and stops it."
    "孝之助一边保持着恶作剧的态度，{p}一边踉踉跄跄地走到节拍器旁，{p}把它停了下来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2016
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_073751a6:

    # "With the metronome turned off,{p}the school is silent again."
    "节拍器的声音消失了，校舍又再度恢复寂静。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2017
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_db635b00:

    # fn "「Huh? Kounosuke, where's Shun-kun?」"
    fn "「对了？{p}孝之助，峻君呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2021
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_8b739010:

    # ko "「Eh? Oh, he's below us.」"
    ko "「哎？{p}啊啊，在楼下」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2025
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0580e537:

    # to "「Wait, why did you leave him behind!?」"
    to "「你把他扔那儿了吗！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2026
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0eb83dd5:

    # ko "「If the two of us needed to escape,{p} I would lie in wait untill morning.{p} So I asked him to wait in the hallway.」"
    ko "「因为万一你们两个人都逃跑了，{p}我还不得再埋伏一夜呀。{p}所以我让峻在门口处待命。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2027
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_45e1e6b8:

    # fn "「Irresponsible as ever...」"
    fn "「还是那么不负责呀……」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2028
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_97def751:

    # ko "「But I made sure to give him a flashlight!」"
    ko "「但是我把手电筒给他了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2032
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c602f245:

    # to "「Still, why did you leave him behind?」"
    to "「所以你就扔下他自己走了？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2036
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_25be3018:

    # ko "「That's...」"
    ko "「那是因为.....」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2037
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_5f4caecf:

    # fn "「Enough of that,{p} let's just hurry and find Shun-kun.」"
    fn "「比起说那些，{p}还是赶紧去峻那边吧」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2041
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_8c04af12:

    # ko "「Th-th-that's right!{p} That's a good idea, [fn]!」"
    ko "「对对！{w=.3}没错！{p}博行说得太对了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2046
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_9fc525f9:

    # to "「Ah, don't try to get out of this!」"
    to "「啊！喂！{w=.3}不要跑！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2047
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_83242552:

    # ko "「Hurry, hurry. Let's go to Shun-kun.」"
    ko "「快...快到{p}峻君那里去！出发！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2051
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_1ff8c9a0:

    # to "「Jeez, that guy...」"
    to "「那家伙真是.....」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2052
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_d9e6549b:

    # fn "「Come on, come on...」"
    fn "「好了好了...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2056
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_74ac4209:

    # "I forget the anger I was feeling up to now,{p}and it's replaced with fear once again."
    "虎彦因为生气，把刚才的恐怖全都忘记了，{p}恐惧又重新袭来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2057
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_f4d7025e:

    # "Without grabbing onto my shirt this time,{p}Torahiko stomps after Kounosuke."
    "这次没有抓着我的衣服，{p}虎彦冒冒失失地追了过去。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2058
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_4d5283b8:

    # "Nearly leaving it behind,{p}I close the door to the music room.{p}I get beside Torahiko in a hurry."
    "好不容易变得冷静了{p}关上音乐教室的门后{p}我也慌慌张张地跑到虎彦身边。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2063
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_49b46899:

    # "We join Kounosuke at the bottom of the stairs,{p}who was waiting for us,{p}then the three of us proceed to the first floor."
    "在下楼处和孝之助汇合，{p}三个人一起去到一楼。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2064
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_6c4a8989:

    # "Being lined up like this,{p}is kind of nostalgic."
    "像这样一起走，{p}感觉好怀念。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2065
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_6e030ee0:

    # "In the past,{p}it was mainly on Kounosuke's whim,{p}but us three would go out and do something foolish."
    "以前，{p}虽然主要是孝之助的一时兴起，{p}但我们三个经常一起出去做些傻事。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2071
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c5b7709c:

    # ko "「But that was fun.」"
    ko "「但是很快乐哪~！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2072
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_9eb1f630:

    # to "「We're not having any fun.{p} Right, [fn]?」"
    to "「我们可不快乐！{p}对吧博行？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2073
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_3c4811d5:

    # fn "「Well, it was quite the thrill, wasn't it?」"
    fn "「嘛，虽然有点毛骨悚然，不过感觉也不错吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2077
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c38b4dcb:

    # ko "「You've got an open mind, just as I expected!{p} That's completely different,{p} from a certain someone...」"
    ko "「不愧是博行，心好宽！{p}和某些人{p}完全不一样呢...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2078
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_0086bd43:

    # to "「Did you say something?」"
    to "「你说什么？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2079
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ab5b3f4b:

    # "Without changing his expression,{p}Torahiko squeezes his open hands together."
    "虎彦表情没有变化，{p}但两手却开始握拳掰着指关节。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2083
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c801f297:

    # ko "「N-nothing, nothing...」"
    ko "「什，什么都没说，什么都没说！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2084
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_63c28886:

    # "Always one word too many, Kounosuke."
    "你这家伙话还是那么多呢{p}孝之助..."

# game/day 6.rpy:2088
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_36797b17:

    # ko "「But, it's alright to have a crazy night,{p} every once in a while.」"
    ko "「但是偶尔在夜晚这样吵闹一番，也不错呢~~」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2089
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c59cd416:

    # to "「The school isn't a good place for that,{p} don't you think?」"
    to "「但不要在学校啦！{p}你不觉得吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2093
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ea908b74:

    # ko "「Then should we have our next test...{p} at a shrine?」"
    ko "「那...下次到神社去试胆？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2097
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_2ea13be5:

    # to "{size=+15}「And this is why...」"
    to "{size=+15}「所——以——说——啊——」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2098
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_29dea86b:

    # fn "「Oh, will you two just shut up already!」"
    fn "「啊，真是的，你们两个太吵了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2099
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_d7bb5760:

    # "Somehow, we manage to get to the first floor."
    "不知不觉，到了一楼"

# game/day 6.rpy:2106
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_49224248:

    # "Even though I really hope to see it,{p}Shun-kun's figure is not there.{p}Just the glow of my flashlight."
    "虽然很希望能看到他，{p}但峻君的身影不在那里。{p}只有我手电筒的灯光。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2110
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_3d6f2107:

    # to "「Anybody there?」"
    to "「没有人吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2111
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_88a500fe:

    # fn "「Kounosuke, where's Shun-kun?」"
    fn "「孝之助，峻君呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2112
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_07e42154:

    # "I call back to where Kounosuke is,{p}but there's no answer."
    "我问向身后的孝之助，{p}但他却没有回答。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2113
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_1fc50344:

    # fn "「Kounosuke?」"
    fn "「孝之助？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2114
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_a3eb6f4b:

    # "I look back and there's nobody there."
    "一回头，发现身后没有人。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2115
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_71da07e1:

    # fn "「Eh...?」"
    fn "「哎……！？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2127
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_251480df:

    # ko "「Boo! Surprised?」"
    ko "「哇！{w=.3}吓到了吧！？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2131
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_c83f33fd:

    # su "「Oh, Kounosuke-san, you're so bad.」"
    su "「真是的，孝之助真是恶趣味！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2132
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_48fb21f6:

    # "Then, those two come out from the shadows.{p}They turned off their flashlights,{p}and were hiding."
    "正说着有两人从阴影里出来。{p}他们关上了手电筒，{p}藏了起来。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2136
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_81f834ab:

    # to "「Once again, you disgust me...」"
    to "「你还是没挨揍呢是吧....」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2140
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ea1419e8:

    # ko "「Woah, that didn't go over so well.」"
    ko "「哎呀~{w=.3}还不能接受嘛~！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2141
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_a15ddc8f:

    # fn "「No wonder. That was the second time!」"
    fn "「这已经是，{p}第二回了！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2145
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_6387595f:

    # to "「I'll fix this!{p} I'll make you into the seventh wonder!」"
    to "「不要动！{p}现在就把你变成七大不可思议！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2149
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_9d3cac4d:

    # ko "「Waah! Shun-kun, help!」"
    ko "「呜哇~~ 峻君救我~！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2153
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_ad781d09:

    # su "「Eh? Ahwawawa!」"
    su "「诶？啊哇哇哇哇！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2154
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_be7ed75e:

    # "Torahiko tries to grab Kounosuke,{p}but Kounosuke uses Shun-kun as a shield,{p}and hides behind him."
    "要抓住孝之助的虎彦，{p}但孝之助把峻君当做盾牌，{p}躲在了他后面。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2155
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_f0245447:

    # "Shun-kun is stuck,{p}and doesn't know what to do."
    "峻君不知所措，{p}不知道该怎么办。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2156
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_bfa1b59e:

    # fn "「Hey you two, stop bothering Shun-kun.{p} Besides, at a time like this,{p} why don't you just save it for tomorrow?」"
    fn "「好了 你们两个，让峻很为难呢。{p}而且都这个时间了，{p}不如留到明天再说吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2160
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_258bf614:

    # to "「Aah, alright...{nw}"
    to "「啊啊，说的也是啊...{nw}」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2162
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_6da9eba9:

    # extend "」"
    extend "」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2163
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_e524e710:

    # su "「I've been saved!」"
    su "「得救啦~」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2164
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_e8f3601e:

    # to "「We should finish up soon.」"
    to "「那我们差不多就解散吧。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2170
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_f6fbe5f9:

    # ko "「Roger that.」"
    ko "「了解～」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2180
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_8519f79e:

    # "On the way back,{p}Kounosuke teased Torahiko,{p}and even got Shun-kun involved."
    "回去的路上，互相打闹的孝之助和虎彦，{p}被牵连的峻还有一直调解的我。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2181
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_418008f9:

    # "I tried to calm them."
    "我试着调解他们。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2182
translate chinese_simplified day06_toratest_975f1e60:

    # "This reminded me, before I transfered,{p}it was always like this.{p}I've missed it."
    "这么说，在转校前，{p}经常这样呢~{p}好怀念呀~"

# game/day 6.rpy:2193
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_8aab5fb5:

    # "The stairs on the north side of the school building."
    "校舍背面的楼梯。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2194
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_467c90d8:

    # "The wonder here is called,{p}\"The Spiral Staircase of Evil\"."
    "这里的是七大不可思议之一叫做{p}「魔力的螺旋楼梯」。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2195
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_d5986521:

    # "The stairs are connected to a mysterious space,{p}and if you're just walking them absentmindedly,{p}you will never make it to the next floor."
    "这个楼梯连接着异空间，{p}如果一边想事一边发呆地走，{p}无论如何也走不到下一层。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2196
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_9b6e8d72:

    # "At the landing of the stairs,{p}there are mirrors that lead to the Underworld.{p}If you leap into them, you can go there."
    "别的楼梯转角也有连接着异界的镜子，{p}跳进去的话{p}就能到那边去。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2197
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_3559f2e5:

    # "There are a bunch of other stories like that."
    "还有很多类似的故事。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2201
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_02132e04:

    # su "「I-is this the place?」"
    su "「是...是这里吗？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2202
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_0072ce9d:

    # "He's scared, and clings to me tightly.{p}Yeah, I have to be his senior,{p}so I try to appear confident."
    "峻君因为害怕，紧紧的跟着我。{p}嗯，作为年长者，{p}要让他看到我威风的样子。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2209
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_131beb6e:

    # "To be honest, I am a little scared,{p}but I keep a calm facade.{p}I set up my camera to take a picture."
    "说实话我也有些害怕，{p}不过表面上还是装得很冷静，{p}并用照相机拍着照。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2210
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_b557f397:

    # fn "「Is this okay?」"
    fn "「这样就可以了吧？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2211
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_2b17532e:

    # su "「I think it's good.」"
    su "「我想可以了...」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2212
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_56a16704:

    # fn "「Then let's go to the next place.」"
    fn "「那我们去下个地方吧！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2216
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_c666627f:

    # su "「Okay!」"
    su "「好！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2217
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_6e1965e5:

    # "Whether it's because I'm trying to appear excited,{p}or I'm trying to appear scared,{p}I hold out my hand and he firmly grasps it."
    "也许是因为害怕，也许是因为兴奋，{p}他紧紧的握着我的手。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2218
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_beffeaf4:

    # "The two of us head up the stairs."
    "两人向楼上走去。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2219
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_21ebc024:

    # "This isn't the kind of place...{p}you would go on a date at...{p}Wait, why am I even thinking about that!?"
    "这又不是约会的地方...{p}不对，我为什么在想这个！？"

# game/day 6.rpy:2220
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_585ed818:

    # fn "「By the way, Shun,{p} there's something I've been wondering about.」"
    fn "「说起来，{p}我有点在意一件事。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2224
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_87b26f8a:

    # su "「What is it?」"
    su "「什么呢？」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2225
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_dd5e7019:

    # fn "「Did you not know what the Seven Wonders were?」"
