    fn "「啊，没事。{p}这个看起来是新的人体模型。」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2429
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_df66e813:

    # "Unaware of it,{p}my reply is dilligently cheerful."
    "虽然不是因为注意到了他的害怕，{p}但还是努力给他爽朗的回答。"

# game/day 6.rpy:2430
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_1c3b7ac2:

    # fn "「If you think about it normally,{p} there's nothing surprising about it!」"
    fn "「随便地考虑下，{p}也没有什么特别吃惊的地方呢！」"

# game/day 6.rpy:2431
translate chinese_simplified day06_shuntest_a8484a6e:

    # "Hahaha, I look over and laugh,{p}Shun-kun also seems to be relieved somehow."
